\id MAT
\ide UTF-8
\h Matta
\toc1 Matta
\toc2 Matta
\toc3 mat
\mt1 Matta
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Bifimer naniya Yecu Kiritti bibwe Dauda, bibwe Abrahame.
\v 2 Abram co te Icaku, Icaku te Yakub, Yakub te Yahuda kange Yitub ceb.
\v 3 Yahuda co te Farica Kange Jera fiye Tamar wiye, Farica nyori te Hacruna. Hacarua co te Arame.
\v 4 Aram co te Aminadabe, Aminadab co te Nacone, Nacon co te Calmone.
\v 5 Calmon co te Buaja fiye Rahab wiye, Boaja co te Obida fiye Rut nine. Obida co te Yeece.
\v 6 Yecce co te Liya Dauda, Liya Dauda co te Culemanu fiye wii Yuriya wiye.
\v 7 Culemanu co te Rehobwame, Rehobwam co te Abija, Abija co te Aca.
\v 8 Aca co te Yehocafa. Yehocafa co te Yorame, Yorame cote Uziya.
\v 9 Uziya co te Yotame, Yotam co te Ahaze, Ahaz co te Hezekiya.
\v 10 Hezekiya co te Manacca. Manacca co te Amone, nyori Amon co te Yociya.
\v 11 Yociya co te Yekoniya kange yitub cebo, dong-dong fiya cuwo ci yem ci, ci yaaken kici biten Babila.
\v 12 Bwiko ci yem ci, ci yaken ci biten Babila. Yekoniya co te Ceyaltiyele. Ceyaltiyele co te Zarubabele.
\v 13 Zarubabel co te Abihudu. Abihudu co te Eliyakime, nimre Eliyakim co te Azuru.
\v 14 Azuru co te Caduku. Caduku co te Akimu, nire Akimu co te Aliyudu.
\v 15 Aliyudu co te Ali'azara, Ali'azara co te Matana. Nimre Matana co te Yakube.
\v 16 Yakubu co te Yucubu bwe Maryamu wo fiye ci wiye ci bo Yecu wo ci cuwo ti ki Almaciu.
\v 17 Core tau Ibrahim nin yaken ciko Dauda nineu kaltito kwob culombo naar, kange wo tau fiye yeka ciko ci yaken ki ci Babilau yaken ciko Kiritti nin, kaldo kwob culombo naar.
\v 18 Bor Yecu Kiritti ko bwi nyo wo. Nece Maryamu ciya an nam Yucufu, naci nakangiri Maryamu kweri tum fer yuwa tangbe wucake.
\v 19 Yucufu bwece nii cakcake, cuibo ci neco kwenduwe nuwe nobe, nyori cuiti naci nyangum kang cinen daar.
\v 20 La ci kwa diker buro tiri, bibwe tomange kwama wucake cerkangu cinen mor dukume. yi coti “Yucufu bi bwe Dauda nuware tai, tum Maryamu wimwe, wori dike ci tum ciko fwereu ca fiya yuwa tangbe wucake nen.
\v 21 can do bwe, mwa cuwo dencere ki Yecu, co ca fulo nubo ti fiye bwiran ker ciye.
\v 22 Gwam wo an bwi na dim diker teluwe be toke nyii nii tomange, tokti ki,
\v 23 “To bubya an tu fwer, naci bo bwe ciya cuwo den cero ki Imanuel” Dike dendo nungeu “Kwama wi kange bo”.
\v 24 Yucufu kwenu dumbo nineu, maani na wo bwe tomange kwama yiceu, cin kuni con tu wice.
\v 25 Yucufu Nyomombo wice wi co bom bwe La con co dendo Yecu.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Bwikako ci bo Yecu Baitalami biten Yahudiya ki core wo Hirudu Liyau, Kangem nob nyomka bifumer kwama bo Urcalima. Tokti ki.
\v 2 “Fee wo ci bo Liya Yahudawa? nyon to bitiren cero twar, nya bo na nyi wabka.
\v 3 La Liya Hiridu nuwa nyori, kwom co kambo ken kange hwam nubo Urcalima.
\v 4 Hiridu mwer Liyab wabe kwama gwam kange nob mulankab nibe. me ci “kiriti a bo fe?” Cin yi co.
\v 5 “ Mor Baitalami Yahudiya nyo won co dike bibei tomange kwama mulange”.
\v 6 “Mo Baitalami mor biten Yahudiya mo kebo wo duwal-duwali tiber Liyab yahudiya. more mwe an fiya nii a ca Liyar tiye wo a yila nii biyuwar nobo Lomi Iciraila”.
\v 7 La Hiridu cwo nob nyomka bifumer reu, yurangum Yurange, me ci “Fiyang bitiren do cerkanguwe?”.
\v 8 Con twom ci Baitalami, yiciti, “Kom ya ki fuwa bwe biduware ki Lima ki Lima, no kom fiya ri, ko bou kom yiye, na mo ken nan ya nan wabco.”
\v 9 Bwikako ci nuwa diker Liya yi ciye ri cin kwen ci ta nure, bitiren do wo ci to twareu yakenti ka ci ya yan titi dor luwe bwe bi duware wiye.
\v 10 La ci to bitirndo ri cin bilangi ki bilankako dur.
\v 11 Cin do mor luwe, nen cin to bwe bi duwareu kange nece Maryamu. cin cung bitine cin wabco. cin kwim cwaye ciye neco Lima nerek, mwinek kange lubban kange mor.
\v 12 Kwama yi ci mor dukume, ciya yilare fiye Hiridu nine. yori cin yilaken bitine ciye nure kange.
\v 13 Bwikako ci kweneu cin to nii tomange teluwe cerkangu Yucufu nin yi co, “Kwen tu bwe bi duwae wo kange bece cwa cu ciko biten Masare.
\v 14 Kume cuwo Yucufu tu bweu kange nece u Masar. yi ken firen yinen di na nimre, wori Huridu cuiti na twalum bweu.
\v 15 Cin yike fire Hiridu Bwiyati. Wo na dim diker teluwe be tokeu nyi nii tomange, “Min cuwou bi bwemi Masar”.
\v 16 Hiridu to nob nyomka Bifumereu bwanten bo ker cero ri mam funer ducce, cin twomi a twalangum bi bei nabarubbe bi duwartini gwam, wo Baitalami kange buro bi dom kange ce tati coro yob yirau ciko bitine.
\v 17 Fiya cuwo la dike nii tomange Irimiya toke dimme.
\v 18 Cin nuwa diro kange Rama ci wiye ti kinero fir cilong-cilonge, Rahila ci wiye dor bi beiyo locer. Mani ca fiya birum nere ti wo mani.
\v 19 Fiya cuwo Hiridu bwiyame, nii tomange teluwe cerkangu Yucufu nin mor dukume mansar. yi co,
\v 20 Kweni tu bwe bi duwarewo kange nece yakan Iciraila, nyori niwo do dume bwetiye bwiyam”.
\v 21 Yucufu kweni tu bwe bi duware kane nece cu biten Iciraila.
\v 22 La ci nuwa Akilayu bi bwe Hiridu Ca liyar ti biten Yafudiya, con nuwa tai lakako firen. Bwikako kwama yi co ker mor dukume, cin tiyangum biten Galili.
\v 23 Yiken fiye kange ci cuwo ti ki Nazaret wo na dim dike ci toki nyii nob tomange ki, “Ciya cuwo co ki bwe nazare re.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Kume ni wo Yuwana yu mwem kwamam tiyeu yau ne fulen ker kwama ro ti.
\v 2 Ko yiloten wori, liyar do lo kwama dadom.
\v 3 won co wo nii dukume kaya tok kerce reu, “Dir nii kanger co bi cor ti kii, toki, “ko Yuwel Teluwe nin nureceu, fuwak ceko atim.
\v 4 Yuwana merum ki belle yiri teleme, bwam ki dk teak fer cer. Cari ceu, kwake kange yuiti to kiyeu.
\v 5 Co rubo Urcalima kange wo Yahudiya gwam, kange bitine tinim bo kong Urduneu, ci bou ti ka bo ka tuje co wiyeu.
\v 6 Na ci yuu cinen mwem kwamam caji Urdun, kambo ci tok bwira kerer ce tiyeu.
\v 7 La co to Faricawa kange cadukiyawa kila cirangum ti na co yu'u cinen mwem kwamamedi co ca ciye, “Kom berin nacuwe ki mwan neu, we wer kom ko cuam funero wo au tiye.
\v 8 Ko ne bituti wo a nung yila ka kume ko tiyeu.
\v 9 Ku kware mor ne kume kom ki Abram te kume! be ma yi kom ti, kwama wi kibi kwan do wo a kung Abram nin bibeiti fo tetendo wuro neneu.
\v 10 Na wonyeu yoti biteye dimer tiniro nan, na cori tiyowo ne bo bituti keneti, an tom co na merken mor kire.
\v 11 Ma Yukumen mwem kwamam bo ki mwem, ya ciko yo laka kumekeu. Niwo bouti bui mi yeu layeki dur, woro ta ceu ma labo nan tu'u. co ca yu'u kumen mwem kwamam bo ki yuwa tangbe kwama, kange kira.
\v 12 Kwele yu'u ka ceko tam kang cek, can nyinagum teneu wiyak, na murom bikateceu na yo ken binico.”
\v 13 La Yecu bou biten Galili, ya caji Urdun fintange Yuwana nen, na yu'u cinen mwem kwamam.
\v 14 La Yuwana mani naco kicim co, tok ti ki, mo wo ma cuiti na yu'u mwem kwamam meu, mom bou minen?”.
\v 15 Yecu yila yi co a ma nyo na dim cak-cakeu gwam. Co Yuwana ciya cinene.
\v 16 Buiko ci yu'u cinen mwem kwamam be di, Yecu cerum can duwo mor mwenge, La dii kwama wo cinen. La co to yuwa tangbe kwamako yirau ti docer na nagumfiye, yira yiti dorcer.
\v 17 La diro kange lo kwama ceru toki, wo bi bwemi ma cui cuiyeu, ma nuwa luma cek ti.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 La yuwa tangbek kwamako tu Yecu yaken ciko mor yere na bwekelkele na cuwaco.
\v 2 Bwiko co yi yim Ngakem kakuko kwini na'ar kumeu kwini na'ar di wura tam co.
\v 3 Nii cuwa kako bou cinen yico ki, “No mo bibwe kwamari yi tero wo ayilam cari”.
\v 4 Yecu yila yic mulagum mulange, Nii mani a dwiti ki cari ki kwace ce kange ker kwamar.
\v 5 La bwekelkele to co yaken ciko mor cinan lor wucakeu. La kung ken co dor ku waber.
\v 6 La yii co ki “No mo bibwe kwama ri, mwou bitine wori mulangum-mulange, ki “Can yi bibei tomange ce wucakeu na cer nen” La ci an kungum nen dii mor kani ciye. be na mo kware na mwek ter”.
\v 7 Yecu yi ten co mulangum mulange mani mwa cuwa teluwe mwe kwama ti ko.
\v 8 Tak, di Bwekelkele tu co kungken co bang ko wo cwem-cwemeu, La nung cenen Liyar do kaleweu gwam kange duktanka ciye ko.
\v 9 La yico ki dike wo gwam man neken nen no mon cung cunge mo wab yeri.
\v 10 La Yecu yico ki “kubom fou bwekelkele be mulangum mulange, Wab ka teluwe mwe kwama co win.
\v 11 La bwekelkele dobco, La wo bibei tomange wucakeu bou cinen (wabco).
\v 12 La Yecu nuwa cin tam Yuwanari, con cerum yilan ken Galili.
\v 13 Co dubom Najaret cin yaken Kafanahum, wuro knog caji Galiliyeu, yii ka bitinek Jebulun Kange naftali.
\v 14 wo ma nye na dim kero Icaya nii dukume tokeu.
\v 15 biten Jebulune biten Nabtali wo kong Cajiyeu, kange dinge caji Urdun neu, Galili nob kumtacili.
\v 16 Nubo wuro yim kumtacili yeu, cin to filanko dur, la buro yim wi fiyeceu, knage kakulok bware keu, dor cir fiya filanko ti kweni.
\v 17 La fiyaco di Yecu yoten fulonka ker kwama ro, ko yolaten wori liyaro loh Kwama biyeken bidom.”
\v 18 co yakenti knog caji Galili, con to yitob butib yob, cimon wo co tiki Bitru, kange Andrawu yii ce mer biliyar ti mor caji, cin nobtaka jingeb.
\v 19 Yecu yii ci, kom bou ko buang menten, an yo ka ta men nob.
\v 20 Dang jang ci dubom liyar cero cin buang ten co.
\v 21 La Yecu dubom wi yaken tiri con to ten yitobbo kange ci yob, Yakubu bi bwe Jabali knage Yuwana yii ce, ci yim mor nabire mwenge kange jabal Tee ciye yulang biliyar ceroti.
\v 22 Con co ci dang jang cin dubom nabire mwengeu kange jabali tee ciye, cim bwang ten co.
\v 23 Yecu kentangum Galili gwam, merang cinen ti mor bikur waber, tok fulen ker liyar kwamaro ti twa'a mwanti tiire ti gwam kange nubo nuwabo lumau.
\v 24 La fulen kere ro dor cereu yake kale mor nubo ciriya, co nubo co ci bou cinen ki nubo wo kalati ki wang ki wang kange kwirom bwi kange buro kelkelibo o cinen ti bwiyeu, kange nob juibe, kange nubo kani kange nani bwiyarangumeu, Yecu twm ci.
\v 25 Nubo nawo kila kilau bwang cinen ten Galili kange dika foli kange Urcalima kange biten Yahudiya, yaken ciko dinge Urdun neu.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Kambo Yecu to mwerkang ka nubo ducceri kwiken dor bang-er. La cin yikenwi, nob bwankacebo bou cinen.
\v 2 Wumom mor nerer ciro takri to merang cinen.
\v 3 Bi bwiyer kiniwo bwini na yuwa tangbeceu nyori liyar kwama ki cii.
\v 4 Bibwiyer kiniwo kibwatummeu, wori ciyatin macinen dangnee.
\v 5 Bibwiyer ki nubo wo ki kunne wori kwalito dorbitinero ki cii.
\v 6 Biwiyer ki nub wurab kange dulo mwe wucakke wori atin bwam ki cii.
\v 7 Bibwiyer ki nub cika bwinib wori, atinci bwinicito.
\v 8 Bibwiyer ki nubo nero wucakkeu, wori ciyen to kwama.
\v 9 Bibwiyer ki nubo ki fuwer nerereu, wori a cociki bi biylo kwama.
\v 10 bibwiyer ki nubo wuro cii ne cii dotangeti ker caccaker, liyar kwama ki cii.
\v 11 Bibwiyer ki kom no nubo to komtiri, yila cii ne kom dotange ti ka kaa cii kwakomti kiner kan-nge bi kulentito bwir wo cuwer keceu, kermin.
\v 12 Kom ma bilangtum bo man ki dii kau, wori Bitininge kumeu na dur dii kwama. Nan wo nubo ne bibei tomange dotange biro yii kaale na nyime komeu.
\v 13 Kom mam dor bitinerembo cano mambo lem lumacekori, bi'amanyi na yilau cuko tak? mani ani yilamti kinan'ngen tak dila atin cutan wi na fuwarangum kina nubek.
\v 14 Kom filang dor bitinero kowo cinar loro tom bidukleu mani yurangek.
\v 15 Nubo mani kwer talkire tire dokken mor bulene, nyori ca kunnyii cayo fiye tikacek nane nubo luweu filang.
\v 16 No nyori filang kume k acera kabum nubem ciya tom yorak na ngenek kumekotiyeu naci caklang tee kume wo dii kwama.
\v 17 Km kware komki mabou nan bubam werfun nobto mangebo. ma boubo nan bubamci Dila nan dimci.
\v 18 Wori bilenker miyi komti, diko kange bitineu an dim dila kiker biduwar kakaa denka win wo mani dimti mor bolang atin dim dikero kang.
\v 19 Nawori niwo kimwo duwal duwale mor werfunen wonine kakaa ci merang kangum ciya manyeri, aciioco nawo duwal-duwale mor liyar kwamar.
\v 20 Lari miyi komti miki “cawo-cawo cakcake kumeu tano labo cakcake nob mulangkab kange faricawbori, mani kakadokanti liyar kwamareu.
\v 21 Kom nuwa kam inyi nubo nan duweu, kom taide dor, cano wo twaldoreri cikino cito warka.
\v 22 La min yi kom ti woma funer kange keceri, kino mor cito warka. woyi kece, mun nifiro bwireri! cikino mor cito doka mor kirak kwamak.
\v 23 Nawo nyori mwane funer nerer ti. tanyi landi kwabi kemwe wiki kwomka dorek kange mori,
\v 24 Dubom luman nerok kabum tan nyi lanem, yaa yam mwem. ki kabana, fuwang kangum kange kemwe na nyi me nabou na ne funer nerer mwero.
\v 25 Maa yuelka kange nii kiyangnye mwe kambo mudor nurer yaa kabum bolangem, ka nii kiyange mwe neken nen nii bolange nin nibolange an neken nen nii tomange ciyatin merkennen furcina.
\v 26 Bilinker mi yinenti, mani mwa certi wi firen dila mwatin yati kemero ci bwang mwenten tieu.
\v 27 Kom nuwa toki mare buraka.
\v 28 Dila miyi komti, tona niwo to nawi ye, ki dilanka nuwa keri, cin kweri cin mam buroka kange co mor nerece.
\v 29 Ca no nuwa me cacciyoro an dok nen kottankari, kurangum co, minangwi fiye muwiyeu. La diker win mor ayak cam, ca merbo curen buyet mwero gwam mor kira kwamak.
\v 30 Kakaa kom mweko cacciyero tano atin atim dok nen kottang kari, mwattumco miranwi fiye muwiyeu. wori in La diker win mor a yakcam, kange merka buye mweko gwam kirak kwama.
\v 31 Yilam to ki niwo ywa wice ri, a neco bifumer nyaka kangeko.
\v 32 Dila miyi komti tano wo ywa wiceri, cano nobo dor kangka diker kayakardi, cin yilam kico ni burokak.
\v 33 Kom nuwa ten cin yi ki nubo burombo nan duwoo kom werde weri cwerke, dila kwama werka kumeko kwamanin.
\v 34 Dila miyi kom ti komti kom werde weri di kwamaka wori Nkunjala kwama;
\v 35 kakaa kange dorbitiner fititim nanice, kakaa Wurcalima, wori biten liya dur.
\v 36 Ca bu nano ka werweri ki dor kumerdi, la mani ka dolti kom yilam ki yiri duwekume fuwoje kakaa fije.
\v 37 Dila Ker kumero a yilam NYO Nyo, nonindi 'Nyonin, nyonin. Cano dikero cumweri, kino bwirkonin.
\v 38 Kom nuwa toki ki, Nuwe nyii nue nundo tak nyii nunne.
\v 39 Dila miyi komti kom mare Kwobkangka kange niwo na bwireu, nyiyoco nyeu, no cii malicom dan-nge cattiyereri, kom yilam cinen wineu ken.
\v 40 No ni kannge wii a yakenti ki kiyange kume kabum boulangem meriwori naci yo belle kueri kom netten nii wo lalan kumeko.
\v 41 Cano ni dokkom yam nako kwininugri kom ya kannyace yob.
\v 42 Komne nii wo mekomeu, tak kom kware niwo do naan ti kumeneu.
\v 43 Kom nuwa dike tokeu, mwan cii ni bidome mweu mwanko ni kiye mweu.
\v 44 Dila min yi kom ti kom cii nob kiyeb kume bo, kom kwob nubo nekom dotannge tiye nin dilo kom ma nubowuri, cil komenin bibuyer, komma nubo wo ko kom tiyeu nin dikoro ken.
\v 45 Naweu nakom yilam bibiyo lo tekume wo dikwamau. wori dok kakuko wennii bwirninti kannge nii ken twom wucakke kannge nii maakenin mwom dikwamati.
\v 46 Wori cano kom ki cwi nubowuri cwikom tiyeri, nyii dikedde kom fiya? kebonyo nob yoka doreko matiya?
\v 47 Kume keneu tano kom yarum ka 'Kebkumebri, yekamani la tangece? kobonyo nubo nyombo kwamau matiya?
\v 48 Dila naweu nyi lam nyo kom yilam cikocok nawo tekumu wodiyeu.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Kom yilam yiber dover ko mare luma kume ko kabum nubem be naci tokom, no kom ma nyori, mani ka fiya cuneti fiye tee kume wo dii kwama wiyeu.
\v 2 La naweu, no kama luma tiri kom cure cume kambo nubo bwirko mati ku wabe kannge dor nurereu wori na nubo caklang ci. Bilinker miyi kmo ti cin fiyam nyii diker cero.
\v 3 La tano kama luma tiri kam kume moutkeu anyomde dike kango cattiyero matiyeu.
\v 4 Wori na lumake meko na yilam yurangum yurannge. Tee kume wuro to dikeroti yuragum yurangeu, atin makumen cuner.
\v 5 Tano kmbo ka kwob diloti takeri, kom yilam de na nubo bwirko, wori ci cwikwoka diloti timotiye ku wabece kannge cuga nurek tak, wori na nubo toci. bilenker miyi kom ti cinn fiyam cuner ceko fou kale.
\v 6 La tano kom kakwob dilotiri, kom doken mor kuwe. Kom nungum nyiloko, kom kwobdilo Tee kume wo yurangum yurange an nekom cuner kumero.
\v 7 Ca no ka kwob dilotiri, kom libride diker manki nagenneu. nawo nubo nyombo kwama matiyeu. wori kwanererceu ciyatin cuwa tuuki keticro dukceu.
\v 8 Na weu ko yilamde naci wo Tee kume nyimoum bwini kumero kikinning nanyime kom kenco.
\v 9 Na wori kom kwobdilo nawo Tee bewo dii kwamau, ane den mwero dur wucak.
\v 10 Liyar mwero a dou ner nuber.
\v 11 Ne nyo carto na dume ce kume -kume.
\v 12 Dob Nyinen bwirang kert nyero. nawo nyi dob nubowo ma yinentiyeu.
\v 13 Yare kinya Fiye cuwaka, dila cok nyo nii bwir konin (kanng Liyar kannge bikom liyaret kange duktanka ka na mwe diri diri ati nyo).
\v 14 Wori no kom dob nubori bwira kerer cirori, Tee kume wo dii kwamau an dobkumen ken.
\v 15 Ca no ka dobbo nubonen bwirang keretinin cirori Tee kume mani a dob kumen ti.
\v 16 Nyotak, no kama nyak tiri, kom yilam kitikob na nuwoma mwamangtu tiye kambo nubo bwirko matiyeu, wori ci kwuob kang yirom cimboti wori naci dannyi kabum nubem mwincimen Nyak ti. Bilenker miyi kom ti ci fiyam cuner cero.
\v 17 Dilacano kom ma Nyak tiri kom beltu nuwan der kom nirum tikob kumebo.
\v 18 La nanubo nyumde kom ma Nyak ti, lakan Tee kume wo to dikero kom matiyeu yurangumeu ati makumen.
\v 19 Kom mwerde dor kumero nii cuweka for dor bitinet, fiye kerkere kange cnkume a kanngum tiyeu, fiye nob kubbo bani werti do kuumme.
\v 20 Nyiyoco Nyeu, kom mwer dor kumer kange nii cuwaka firen dii kwama fiye kerkere kannge cankume mani yeu. nawo a kanngum tiye fiye tak nuu kuyee mani werti na kumme.
\v 21 Fiye cuweka mweu wiyeu ner mwero ki nowi ken.
\v 22 Nuweu co talkire bwiyeu. Nawori cno nuwemweu yorari, bwiyo kwarub dimki filang.
\v 23 la cano nuwemweu dikero kendi bwiyo kwarub dimki kumtacile.
\v 24 Nii mani bwiya bwnagten, Tee yobe La catin ciya wi ci ko win mani nyori can ciya kanyenin win ci cuyekangum wiceu.
\v 25 La na weu, miyi kom ti kom kwomre dor yimer kumer kidiki kacati yeu, kannge diker na netiye kakaa bwikume dike kama kulenti cikeu. Naweu dume labo carita, bwiyo labo kulanda.
\v 26 Kom to bilibenti dii kwama maci fi fik kakaa biyeka maci mwerank tak mor bine, Tee kume wo diyeu. No nyori kalancibo yorankka.
\v 27 we more kume a cob dorcero ninten cwemka kumetik kiker dikerowo kwom cotiye?
\v 28 La nya ko kwom dor kumeroti ker kulenerer? kom to funti nimbo kiyeu, kambo ci dwitiyeu. maci du kulent.
\v 29 Gwam kange wuru miti kom ti, culemanu ken mor dukktanka mabo nawin more birombonen.
\v 30 Cano kwma maa yera ko kiyenen bwa yilendi, wuro duwei notiyeu firuri ciyan merken yiri infe Danka Yorakko. kom dobbo dubo ki bwini bilin kerereu?
\v 31 Nawo nyeu ko kwomde kom ki “Ye ba catiye, Ye ba dutiye
\v 32 Na weu nubo nyombo kwama wuyak ci do dukum kulenenmbo woti, Tee kume wo diyeu nyimom kom ti citi.
\v 33 Dila kom do liyar cero ki kaba kannge ladi kulendowo kwarub ciyan nekom.
\v 34 Nawue. kom kwomre dor kumer ko bwikume kwarub kumeniu ci dontanngece.
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 Kom mare warka, na cii makumende Warka.
\v 2 Ki Warkako kom ki wardeu, ciya warmwen ki kwele mwa cuwa, ki kwele cu ciya cuwamwen cuko
\v 3 Ye bwi muto cukkum bwatiye ti nure kemwe dila mutobo we mweu nure mwe?
\v 4 Kaka ca manyi mwayi kemweti Berin cok mwe be dikoro nuwe mwe, wendi cuktom bwatiyeu wo nuwemwe?
\v 5 Mwo nii bwir teri cokum cuktum bwatiyeu nuwe mwe, na yimde mwatin dolum mwan tom yor, kambo mwa cukom cuktum watiye ti nuwe kum mwe
\v 6 Kom nere bicurle dikerowo wucak wucakkeu. la ki kom merde bilerinin cari bwayilenner kumer kebo nyo ri ciya fuawrumci.
\v 7 Kii ni ciya necom do mwatin fiya kwabi tak, an womwen.
\v 8 Ca niwo keneri atin yo, wo kwaberi atin wom ci nen.
\v 9 Kakaa weni more kume, bibwece a kenco Tilitari la a ne co ta tiye?
\v 10 Kakaa no kenco jinge tiri a ne co na cuwetiye?
\v 11 Nyori ca no kom bwirembo, ko yumum kambo kane bibiyo lokume lumako tiye, kambo Tee kume diyeu a ne kom dikero kentiye.
\v 12 Na woro di gwamra dikero kom ci ti nubo amakume neu, kom macinen ken.
\v 13 Kom doken nure wo dwaldwaleu, wori nure buareu kuya in nurewo bwaibo doka nob dokabo moreceu ci kila kabo.
\v 14 Di la nureu yaken dumeu kwati kabo, nureu na wo bwai doka nub fiya kaceco kila bou.
\v 15 Kom nyimi ki nob tomangeb dukumeb cuer kobe burombo bokumentiki curen kwamereu, bilinke cin nyece-nyece burombo kuyamtiye.
\v 16 Ka tin nyumom ci kibi tuttuice nubo cok mwembo twiber ko bwi cuike kakaa nying bwi cilannge ka.
\v 17 Nyo kwarub Tini yoken kitu bi tuttuie ken tiyo bwirko ki tuttuice bwir.
\v 18 Tiyo yoryoreu mani tu bi tuttwi bwirti, yo tak tiyo bwir mani tu bi tuttwiy ken.
\v 19 Tano tiyowo mani ne bituttuti kentiyeri laciya tom ciya merken mor kire.
\v 20 La nyori kin duku bibiyem bowo anyomcitiye.
\v 21 Kebo nubo wuyak yiye tiki Tee, Tee adokenti o kwama dila niwo bwanteng ker tee mire dii kwama.
\v 22 Ki ka koko wo ducce an yi ki Tee, tee nyori nyamabo ker dukkumer kiden mwer nya cobo niya kiden mwer. nya mabo nangen do durbitineu ducce kiden mwera?
\v 23 La man yici ma yomkombo ko dubomye, kom nob make bwira kerer.
\v 24 La naweu Manang cemen cukotakeu, can dang kengco na ni nyomka wuro mu kuceu bangereu.
\v 25 La mwembo cuweri yuwako kunou kwa luweu dila yarbo wori ci muco dor bangek.
\v 26 Di la niwo nuwa kermirori mabo nange cike, ciya dan co kannge kulenii wo mu loceu dorbi ti nere.
\v 27 Mwembo cuire mwem wurmamkako bou dila yuwa ko kwenu kwa luwe yalam bukti.
\v 28 La kambo Yecu dim tokka keti ceri mwerkan kako nyimang merang ka ceko.
\v 29 wori meran ci nen ti ki bi kwan liyarer, kebona mulangkab.
\c 8
\p 
\v 1 kambo Yecu yirau do doweri nubbo ducce bwancinenten.
\v 2 La nii ki wale kung diro kibi kwan ki no mwi ciu tiri mwatin yilam kimo wucak.
\v 3 La Yecu tar kang ceko kico ri ki “miki cui”. La yilam wuccak, la dang jang dang jang cii yilam wucak ki wale ceu nen.
\v 4 Yecu yico “yire nii ka nge diker” tame nureu ya nung dormwero nii wabenin na mwi ne lumacere ko werful muca ko tokeu. wo buka kanger ce ko.
\v 5 kambo ci yilau ti kafanahum meri, nii dur nob kweneo bou cinen ken coti.
\v 6 La ki Te luwe bwe canga dam lo kilen di la nuwa dotange ti kambo ken.
\v 7 Di la Yecu yi c o “Matin bou nami twam co”
\v 8 Nii dur nob kweneb bo ciya co ki “Teluwe mi labo wo mwi bou to lo miyeu. Tok kaker dila bwe canga ni atin twam.
\v 9 wori no mo ken min nii ciyo dur biwan keret, tag ri min wiki nob kwenebo min dur dor cere. Miki yi w miki ya ri ci yaken, ki kanage 'bou ri ci bow kange ki canga mi, ma wuro dila cimam.
\v 10 Kamo Yecu nuwa weri, cin nyi mangi la cin yi biro bwang cinnen ten tiyeu, “bilenker mi yi kom ti mi fiya bo kange win wo ki bilenker nawo mor Iciraila.”
\v 11 Min yi kom, kila atin bou twaar kange me la ciyan ca wari kange Ibrahim, Icaku kange Yakubu mor Liyar kwamar.
\v 12 Yilo bibei liyareu atin cor ke mor kumta cilero kiring kiring fiye cika wiyek kange kika nuneg?
\v 13 Yecu yi dur nor kwenebo, “ya nawo mwi le bilenkeu, la a mamwen nyo dila cnagau twam ki kwama don-dong (Yila mwenyo).
\v 14 kambo Yecu bow mor lo Bitruce ri cin to fer Bitruce nawi yeu dam da nuwa luma ki kwi bwi.
\v 15 Yecu tai kang cekori la kwirom bwim bo dubom co. Dila cin kweni cin ter maka cinen carito.
\v 16 Kambo meu dome ri nubo bow Yecu ki nubo kila wo ki kelkelitini yeu. Ciin cikangum yuwa tangbe tinito ki ker yila cin twam wiyak biro nuwabo lumau.
\v 17 Ki nure wo la diim digero toku nyi kaya nii tomange, tokti ki “co ciki bwico yem bwii nuwa ka luma beko ri yila cin tum twirak beko”.
\v 18 L kambo Yecu to mwerkako duce ken tangum ceri cin neci nyal naci yabken kong wimak ko Galili.
\v 19 La ni mulankak bow cinen di to ki ki, “nii meraanka, matin bwang mwentn {Bwen no mwiki yang fye mwi yakenti wiyeu gwam feri}”.
\v 20 Yecu yi co ki” wiki buwak cek, kange bilibetinim wo dii kwamau wiki lo cece dila bi bwe nii fire mani ki fiye wo ci yom dor tiye.”
\v 21 kange mor nub bwang kab cebo yico, “Teluwe dob ye bwiri nan ya nami fwerum teni”.
\v 22 Di la Yecu yi co ki “Bwangmenten na dob nubo bwiyamen na fwerum bar cero.
\v 23 Kambo Yecu dogen tukom bwatiyeri, nob bwangka cebo bwang ci nen ten more ce.
\v 24 La yuwako durko kwenu mor wima, tokum bwantiyebo cimon ki yuwa mwengeb. La yecu dam dum.
\v 25 Nob bwang kab ceko bow cinen di yunco tokti ki “Cer nyo Teluwe, yan bwiya rangum.
\v 26 Yecu yi ci “Ye bwi kom cua tai tiye, kom wo ki bilenkere biduwaru?” Di la cin kweni la werang yuwako knge wimau. la cinge dur tam.
\v 27 Nubo nyimangi la ciki “nage nii ko wini wuro, wo ki yuwa ce kange wima nuwa co tiye?”.
\v 28 Kambo Yecu bow dinge wineu kange mor biten gadara nubo yob wo ki ninga tininyeu wab kam co. ciki ceru mor tuwe, la ci bwi kabo wo nob yameb mani cu nure wiyeu.
\v 29 La cin kwa kiyakye ki dir cin yi ki “ye yo nen kange nye, bibwe kwama? mwi bo fo namwi nenyo dotange nanyumde kwama nye lauwa?”
\v 30 La nyere tini duce ca canak ti fiye co, kwitangbo ducce kange fiye ci niyeu.
\v 31 Ninga tini tii kinito Yecu nin ciki “No mwi coknyori, tungen nwo mor nyere tini.
\v 32 Yecu yi ci “ko ya” la ninga tininu ceru yila dogen mor bentilen nyeretini, la bentilen nyeretiniu yirarangu kulor dugleroni di corge mor wima cin bwirangum mor mwege.
\v 33 Nubo to nyere tiyeu cin cua cin cu dila cin yaken mor cinar lor la cin yici digero bwiyeu wiyak. diger fiya nubowo ki ninga tiyeu.
\v 34 La cinartoro wiyak ceru naci wabkan Yecu. kambo ci to ceuri cin kinong co ca dubom cunga ceko.
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Yecu dogen nabire mege, yabken dingeri la cin bou mor cinanlor cer.
\v 2 La cin bo cinen ki kilen niir dam dor bicirit ki, toka bilen keret cero ri, Yeu yi kilen mire, “Bwe, bim ner. bwiran keretini mweron tabum cuko.
\v 3 La knagem nob mulangab toki bwiti ci, “nii wo na dur ti”.
\v 4 Yecu nyumom diger ci kwati ner cereu cn yiki “Ye bwi kom kwa digero bwiti ner kumere?
\v 5 Na wini bweibe, a tokki bwiran kertni meu tabum, kaka a tiki 'Kweni ti na ya yambo?'
\v 6 Di la nako nyimori bibwe nii fire wiki bikwan keret dur kaler na tabum bwirangker, “ci yi kiledo, “Kwenti tum biciri mweu na yaken lomo”.
\v 7 Di la nii cou kweni lan cu gen loco.
\v 8 Kambo nubo mwe rumweu to eri, cin cwatai ri cin duktan kwama, wo ne nubo bikwan nerero naweu.
\v 9 Kambo Yecu cuken fiye ceri, cin to nii dndo Matta yim fi yime nob yoka nob yoka dorekke. cin yico “Cin yi co bwangmenten” la cin kwani cin tiri cin bwangcinnenten.
\v 10 Nawo Yecu yiken caka cari mor luweri, dila nob yoka dorego duce nob bwangketi bow la ca wori kange Yecu kange nob bwangkab cero.
\v 11 Kambo nob diklingebo to weri cin yi nob bwangkabo ceko “Ye bwi nii merangka kume ko ati wari kange nob yoka dorek kange nob bwirangkere?”.
\v 12 Kambo Yecu nuwa na weri, cin ki nubo we kwamer mor bwiyam mani cui nii twaka, kanco nubo wo nuwa bo lumau.
\v 13 Yom ya na kom merang digero wo nung tiyeu: “Miki cui nuwa ka bwinik la kebo twika nuwange go ficange. ma boubo nan co cakcak na yiloten, dila nob bwirangkereb.
\v 14 La nob bwangka Yuwanako bow cinen, ciki, “Ye bwi nyo kange nob diklingebo yiti ngag kang kangri la nob bwangka mwe ko mani yiti ngag ngage?
\v 15 Yecu yici “Bibei nange ne ku duklume tin ci wiye ki kwamawo nii bineu wari kange ciye? Di la kumetini ber wo ciya tum nii bincu ti cine neu la ciya tin yi ngag ngag.
\v 16 Nii mani a yoten fiti kwele fwirti dor kwilenero car wori fiye tabeu atin woram bwi kwileneniu rila worakako atin bwira.
\v 17 Kaka nubo kiyo mwem bituituinbo fwir mor bantilando car. No ci mani nyori, bantilando atin wurom ri mwem bo tuituinbo atin curi la bantillando wurom. nyori ciki yo bwem bi tuituinbo fwir ko mor bantilando fir ri naci lere kange ce.
\v 18 Kambo Yecu tok digero biro tiyeri, la nii dur bow cung cinen. riki” bwe bubiya miu bwam na wonyo dila bow yoti kang mweko cinenn naci kwenim.
\v 19 La Yecu kweni bang cinenten kange nob bwangka ceko.
\v 20 La nawiye kange wo kala ti cor ka bwiyalecu coro kwob cilombo yobeb bow bwingob Yecu la cin ke nyi kwilencero.
\v 21 Ri cin yi dor cero, “tano matin teyim ka kwilencerori man yilam kwamer”.
\v 22 Di la Yecu yila kangi lan to co, “Bwe Bubiya” bim ner, bilenke mweu twamnen”. la nawiyeu fiya twaka dangjang. (Ki kwama co.)
\v 23 Kambo Yecu bou lo nii durreu, cinto nubo cu lira tiyeu kange nubo dimeu ma dike ti duce.
\v 24 Ciki “ko yakenti Bubiyau bwiyabo, dila ciki da dum. “Di la ciin nunco ki cuekanka.
\v 25 Kambo ci cokken nubo kaleri, cin dogen kuwenin la cin tau co ki kang, la Bubiyau kwenim.
\v 26 La kerowo yalati cinanlor cunga ko cuew.
\v 27 Kambo Yecu cungenti fiye ceri, fugma tini yob bwang cinen ten. cin tii kwaka direko la ciki, “nuwa bwini nyero, Bi bwe Dauda?
\v 28 Kambo Yecu bow mor leuweri, fugma tinimbo bow cinen. Yecu yici, “Kom ne bilenke matin ma diker wa?” cin yico ki “Og Teluwe”.
\v 29 Di la Yecu ke nuwe cue ri ki a yila kumen dong dong bikwan bilenkerer kumer”.
\v 30 La nuwe cue womagum Di Yecu neci bi werer kibi kwan, “Nii kange a nyomde diker dor wo”
\v 31 La nubo yobeu cerken wam kero dor dikero wo cunga ko cuo nin.
\v 32 Kambo nubo co yobeb yaken tiri cin bou Yecu nen ki nii wo tabang tabange ker ti ki ningau.
\v 33 Kambo ci cukom nigari nii wo tok ker la na nubo dimmeu nyimangi ri, “Nii tombo dikero wo wi biten Iciraila?”
\v 34 La nob diklingebo tok ki “ki bi kwan iyar niga ci cikang ninga tiye.”
\v 35 Yecu bwangten cinar lor gwam kange cunukur cin cakaba ki meranka mor bi kur wabka ci tok fulen ker liyaret kange twakak dimer ni twirakeo gwam kange lumako nubo neneu gwam.
\v 36 Kabo cito mwerka nubekeri cin nuwa bwini cero, cin nuwa dotange tiri cin cwam tai. ki “Kwama wo man ki nii toci tiye.
\v 37 Cin yi nob bwanka ce ko “Biyeka bitok ko duce ri la dob nangenebo kilabo.
\v 38 La nyori ko kwob dilo wulom Teluwe beka, ko bitok ko nii nacin tung nob nagenebo mor biye ka bi tok ceko nin.
\c 10
\p 
\v 1 Yeco co nob bwangka wari, la cin neci bikwan keret dor yuwa tangbeko bwir naci cukangwi ci, kane naci twam tuwirantini gwam kange nuwarangka luma ko maniyeu gwam.
\v 2 La den nubo tomangebo kwob cilombo yobeu co buro ki kabou Cimon (wo ci cou tak ki Bitru) kange Andirawu kece, Yakubu bi bwe Zabadi, kange kece Yuwana.
\v 3 Filibu, kange batalamawu, Toma, kange Matiyu nii yoka dorek, Yakubu bi bwe Alfa, Kange Taddawu.
\v 4 Caminu Bakairawau, kange Yahuza Ickarioti wo miyem Ceu.
\v 5 Kwobcilombo yobeu wo Yecu tomci cin yici ki nyal la ciki, “Ko yare fiye kange wo nubo yim kumtacileu, kom dore kange cinanlor nubo Camariya.
\v 6 Ko ya nyori kwame wo lo Iciraila lem meu.
\v 7 La kambo kom ya kom yii fulenker kom ki Liyar kwamak bow bidom.
\v 8 Ko Twam wo nuwabo lumau, kon kungum wo bwiayameu, nako cokum ten ninga. lima nee ko yoke ko neken ki lima neek.
\v 9 Ko tur kange mwin, azurfa kaka tagulla mor cuwaye kime.
\v 10 Ko ture cuwaye Yam kimembo ce, kaka kulen, kaka taa wori nii nagenne daten cari cor.
\v 11 Ki cinan loro kaka mwan loro ka doweri, ko do nii datenne more ce, ko cer locona nyim de ko dob fiye co.
\v 12 Kambo ko do mor luweri, ko ma yarume.
\v 13 No luweu da tendi kom dob fur neret kumeu ayirati, no ci datenbori fur neret kumero ayilau kumen.
\v 14 Nubo wo yo kombo kaka cuwa tu nuwa ker kimereu, Kambo kom cerum luwe nen kaka cinan lor cero ri kom fugom kwerdo nakume keu nen.
\v 15 Bi lenke miyi komti Biten codoma kange Gomara atin fiya jire duwe ki kakuk bolanger kange cinan loro co.
\v 16 To min Tomkom na kwame mor ngece ngece, ko yilam kiyiilam na nacuwe tini ri la ko wii re na nagum fe?
\v 17 Ki yi ki bati kange nubo, ciyan neken kob kan nob yimnom dila ciya tin malliki kom mor bikur wabeb cer.
\v 18 Ciyan bou ki kom kabum nob bolangeb kanage liya, ker mir na warkan cinen kange nubo yim kuntacileu.
\v 19 Kambo ci neken komeri kom kwom de ki kambo kange dikero ko tok tiye, wori atin nekom di diker ko tok tiyeu ka kwama co.
\v 20 wori kebo kom ko tok ker tiye, dila yuma tangbe te kume a tok kerti kumene.
\v 21 Kece atin ne ken kece nai twalum, dila Tee ceu bibwe ce. Bibeyo atin kwinag Teb cebo nen tien ci doki ci twallagum cii.
\v 22 Nubo duce an ko kom ker denen miir. Dila wo mwirom yaken ciko di ka ri ni cou atin fulo ka.
\v 23 No ci nekom dotange cinar lor wori koom cuaken cinan loro bdomeu, la miyi km bilenke ti, mani kom kentange cinan loro Iciraila ti wiyak nangimde bibwe nifire n bou.
\v 24 Ni bwanka duwi bo la nii merrang cinen tiyeu kaka canga dor Teeluwe ce.
\v 25 Dong dong ni bwanka a ylam a nii merang a ceko, kange caga na teluwe ce. Ta no cin cou Tee luweu Ba'al zabuba ri, la an bwira dendo wo ciya com numo loceu ti cike.
\v 26 Nyori, ko cua cire, wori yurke mani wo mnaiya tok tiye, kange dikero mni wo yurangum yurangeri mani a coku ti yanglang.
\v 27 Di kero mayi kom kumta cileu ko toki ki Kakkuk kange dikero mwi nuwa bi luma mor tuwe meu, toki ki dir dor lor.
\v 28 Cuwa re nubo wo twallum bwiyo ri la mani a twal dume tiyeu. Na wori cwa ni wo a twallum bwiyo ti kange dume mor kira kwama.
\v 29 Kebo bilibe yob ci miyeti dor wina? Duwal kange ce man o a yarti bilineri kebo ymka Teku mek.
\v 30 La yiri duwe kumeu kiyem kiye.
\v 31 Ko cuwa re tai km la bilibetini yroka.
\v 32 La nyori gwam niwo ne warke me nuwe nuberi matin na warke ce ken kabum temim wo dii kwamau.
\v 33 Niwo ko neka warke dor miir kabum nuberi mo ken man neka warke dor ceer ka Tee mii wo dii kwama.
\v 34 Ko kware komki min yau ri nami bou ki fuwor neret dor bitinr. I yau bo nabi bou ki fuwor neret, dila kulen.
\v 35 Min bou na mi dok nii kiye kange tece, kange Kiye biber bubiyak kange nece kange bifire bwe bubiya kiye kange fer e nawiyeu.
\v 36 Nii kiye niu atin yilam co wo mor luwe ceu.
\v 37 Co wwo cui tece kaka nece laye re ri daten bo na mii wo ciu bwe kaka bwe bubiyaceu, layere da ten bo na mii.
\v 38 Co wo tu bo kwoblom bwatiye ce na bwang men teneri daten bo mii.
\v 39 Nii wo cui ti naci fulo dume ceri, an lem dume ceu. la wii dume ceu kermireri an fiyam co.
\v 40 Wo yokomeri yo mo, dila nii wo yo yerri, yo co wo tomou yereu.
\v 41 Wo yo nii tomange ki den nii tomangeri an yo cuner nii tomangero, la co wo yo nii cak cakke ki den nii cak-cakke ri atin yo cuner niiwo cak-cakeu.
\v 42 wo ne win more bi duwartini buru kwel mwenge yibe nano ki den ni bwangkake ri, bilenke mi yi komti mani a le cuner cero ti”.
\c 11
\p 
\v 1 Bwikako Yecu dim biweret bi bei tomange ceri, cin dibom bi kole cua na co merang, na cin yi ci fulen ker kwama cinnr lor cer.
\v 2 La Yuwana nuwa co fiya co, ci fucinu dikero Yecu matiyeu, con tom bi bei tomange ceu na co yi co.
\v 3 Mon co nii boutiye kaka nyo ningtang kange ka?
\v 4 Yecu yi ci ki, kom ya ko yico dika ka towe kange dike ka nuwa!
\v 5 Fukma ti toi, kilendo yayamti, walebo cin twam ci nubo mani nuwareu to nuwai ci kung nubo bweyameu ti nob bunebo ci neci fulen kerero ti.
\v 6 Nii wo nuwabo funer kange me ri nob bibwiyer.
\v 7 Kambo nubo wuro cuweri Yecu yi nubo mwerumeu ker dor Yuwanar.
\v 8 Ye no kom cer yerak di kom ki tore, Yerako Yuwako moktiya? lan ye ka ciri ka towe nii dum ki kulendo fila-fila? Bilenker nubo dum ki kulendo Fila-fila ki daa lo liyabe.
\v 9 Ye ka ceri ri ka towe bwe tomange kwama? ong mi yikomti, bwe tomange kwama.
\v 10 Wo cowo ci mulang dorcer ki “to mi tom kimen nii tomange miti ka kom nuwe kime, wo a Yulang nure mwe tiye.
\v 11 Min yikom bilenke ba kange ci kung more kime wo natum bowe la Yuwana nii yuka mweme ke. Nyori bi duware gwam mor liyar kwamareu laco.
\v 12 Ta ti kumeni Yuwanan nii yu mwemtiye yau ciko caneu, liyar kwamaro nuwa dotange kwiklki-kwilkiye, nob wilki-wilkiro tu kibi kwang.
\v 13 Fiya na Yuwana na bou gwam nob tomangeb kwamaro kange werfundo tak ker dukumero woti.
\v 14 No mwan ciya mo yuwo ri con Iliya wo a boutiye.
\v 15 wo ki tuweri a nuwa.
\v 16 Ma bonkan kwaldo wo ki ye? ci nabi ma lor ti fiye miyeka dike, wuro yirongm cuwo butici tiye.
\v 17 Toki bin cii mwen lira mwa yelbo yila. Nyo yi kwan bwa, mwe cibo wiye.
\v 18 Wo Yunana bou mani ca cari, ma no nyom kom yi ki to ciki bwekelkele.
\v 19 Bibwe nifire bou, ti cai ti noi ri, kom ki to wi ki nii kucunu knge ni o nyom tiye, far nob yuwaka kiyeme kange nob bwiranke! Nyori yilang ki fiya yuwoka ki nangendo co matiye.
\v 20 La Yecu yoten werang cianr loro wo co man diker nyimankar wiyeu ducceu wori cin yiloka.
\v 21 kwamen mo karangcimun kwamanen mo Baptcaida naki diker nyimankaro wori ci ma kimeneu, cimam taaya kange cindo di, kin yiloten kutan -kutange mor yakca yilanga kange bi tuwam.
\v 22 Na cuwori an la Tayanin kange cidon dor kimer, kakuk bolanger.
\v 23 Mo kafanahum, mo kwatiri man fiya duktonka lo kwama ka? or ong an cukken nen bitine, hadec. mo codom naki nyimangeu manue, ma muneg di, no ki wi duwal.
\v 24 Mi yikomti a yilam bwai biten codome min, na kimeu.
\v 25 Ki fiya co Yecu toki, “Min cakakom ti, Tebe, teluwe lo kwama kange kaleu, wori kom yurangen dike buro ka fiya nob yalannereu kange nyomka, la ka wom biyeyo bi dwartini nineu.
\v 26 Ong, te wuro yori kaba nuwe mwe.
\v 27 Dikero gwam cin neken ye fiye temi wiya ni kange mani wo a nyom bwe tiye, nyombo teu, nyo tak ni kange mani wo a nyom teu na bi bwece, kange wo co cokum naci nun cinene.
\v 28 Bou minen kom wo ki nuwa dotange tiye, wo ki kulendo tutue, nan ne kom fubi.
\v 29 Tu kulen miro, ki merangi mineng, wori mi lom-com, miki nero yiber mwan fiya fobka dume mwe.
\v 30 Wori kulen miro bwaibo, takeu kulen miro tubo.
\c 12
\p 
\v 1 Ki fiya cuwa, Yecu kwen yam ki kakuk fobka mor tankini. Bibei tomange ceu nuwa wura ti, la ci kwer dor cangero ti citi cai.
\v 2 La fariciyawa to nyori, cin yii Yecu, “To be bei tomange mweu diker ci matiye werfundo ciyabo a mani ki kakuk fobka.
\v 3 La Yecu yi ci ki ka karanta bo diker Dauda mane kange nobo loce ki fiya cuwo ci nuwa wura tiya?
\v 4 Con doken bi kur kwamar, con ca cari wiye wo werundo ciya cinenbo kange nobo cineneu, ciyam kin nob wabeb koni.
\v 5 Ka mor werfuna, ki kakuk fobka, nob wabbe kwama mor kikur kwamare ma dike werfundo ciyanbe, nyori, ci tacibe ki kero bwia?
\v 6 Min yi kom niwo la bikur kwamareu wo fo.
\v 7 Na ki ka nyimom ye wuro nuntiyeri, 'miki cwi cire duwe kebo twika nuwange ko wucake, no kom ki warbo ker dor niwo man ki bwiran kereu.
\v 8 Bibwe nifire co teluwe kakuk fobka ke.
\v 9 La Yecu dubom bikole cuwo, doken bi kur wabbero Urcalimau.
\v 10 wori, nii kange kanko nom nowe wini. Fariciyawa me Yecu dong dongka a twa ni ki kakuk fobka ka? o na cin taco ki ker bwiranke.
\v 11 Yecu yi ci we fo more kume no kwame ce yarken bouk ki kakuk fobka ri mani a tau ti cokumme?
\v 12 Na wine la kece kwame kaka nifir? nyori werfundo ciya a ma diker ken ki kakuk fobka.
\v 13 La Yecu yi niwo, “Taruu kangeko, la con taruu kang ceko, la kango yilaken kwamer na wineu.
\v 14 La fariciyawa erken kale cin mwer kangi dor Yecu. ciki do nure ciya twalum Yecu tiye.
\v 15 Yecu to nyori co ci dubom bi kole cuwe. nuwe. nubo ducce bwanteng ce, con twam ci.
\v 16 Con yi ciki nyial ciya yire nii.
\v 17 wo na ci dim dike ci tok nyii nii wabe kwabe Icaya, tokti ki.
\v 18 Too Yii tomange me wo ma cok ceu, ma bilankange ceu, Man ne co yuwa tangbek miko naci yii nubo wo kebo Yahudawa.
\v 19 Mani ca kwobkan ker ti, Mani ca ci wiye ti ki diir, mani a nuwa dircer ti nure.
\v 20 Ma ca kyan dike fwinongum ti, ma ca dom kra ko dadom bwiyakau, can ya ki warka turani.
\v 21 Mor dene ce nubo kumtacile an fiya yim yo neri.
\v 22 Nyori cin bou ki nii kange, fukma, mani nuwa tuu, wiki ninga fiye Yecu wiye. Con twam cona wo Nyori nii cuwo tok ker, ti toi tak.
\v 23 Nubo wmerkangum gwamme nuwa nyimangka la me, wo co bibwe Dauda ka?
\v 24 La fariciyaa nuwa diker nyimankako Yecu maneri cin yi ki, “Nii wo ki cok ninga kin bahalzabu liya kelkelebe.
\v 25 La Yecu nyimom dike ci kwati ner cere, yi ci ki, Liyar do wo yalkangum me ri, mani a ti-ti cinar lor tikangum yobe mani a titi, kako luwe fwemme ri, an wurom.
\v 26 No bwekelkele cok bwekele ri ki maa kiiye ki dor cero. La a mangyi na liyar do wo ti?
\v 27 No miki cok ninga kin Ba'alzabu ri, bi bei kimeu ki cok ki ye? nyori ci ciya yila warka kimek tiye.
\v 28 No miki cok ninga ki yuwa tangbe kwama wucake ri, nangi liyar kwamaro bou kimen.
\v 29 A man nyii nii doken lo nii bikwanne na ku kwi, co co bwam cobo ri? na nimre kange me ri ki ma kiiye kange mo, takeu, niwo mwerbo kange me ri, ki watangken.
\v 31 Na wori mi yi kom ti, “bwirangke kange dilanka gwam an curanwi. La dilanka yuwatangbeko wucake mani a curang ti wi.
\v 32 Ni wuro tok dikro bwir dor bibwenifireu a cutang wi wo tok kero bwir dor yuwa tangbe wucakeu a curang cinen ti wi fo kale wo kange wo boutiye.
\v 33 Ywel tiyo a yori, bi tuti ce an yori kaka ywel tiyo a bwira bi tuti ce a bwira.
\v 34 Kom bi bei na cuwe, kom nubobwir a ma nyii ka tok dikero keng tiye? Mor dikero ducce nereu co nyiiyo toktiye.
\v 35 Ni ken ki coku dikero kendo ner cereu, nii bwir ki cok dikero bwir ko ner cereu.
\v 36 Mi yikom ti ki kakuk warka nubo an ne warke dor dikero bwir ko ci toke.
\v 37 Ki kero nyii mweu an coknen ki kero nyii mweu an kuwa nen.
\v 38 Nyori kangem nob mulang kar kange Fariciyawa ciya Yecu nin ki “nii merangka, nyi cwiti nayi to yirom muneng”
\v 39 la Yecu yi ci ki, “Kom nubo bwir, kom nob burotumbo kaldo weu, ko do yirom ti mani k fiya ti no kebo ka wo Yunana nii tomangeu ce ri.
\v 40 Nyori Yunana da kuma taar, kakuko taar mor fwer jingi dur, na cuwo bi bwe nii an daa kume taar, kakuko taar mor bitine.
\v 41 Nubo niniba a kweni an tii kange nubo kaldo we ki kakuk wara, ci an kuwa ci wori cin yiloten ki fulen kerek Yunana ro, la to nii kange wo la Yunana wo.
\v 42 Liya bangeu an kweni kane nobo kaldo, an kuwaa ci. ca bou cile kale wo na ci nuwa yilen Culemanu ro, la to nii kange wo laa Culemanuweu wo.
\v 43 No yuwa tangbe ko bwir cerum nii nen di ki yaya fiyeni wo mwem mani yeu na ci fiya fobke, mani ca fiyati.
\v 44 La yi ki man yilaken lomiyo ma cerueweu. No ci yilaken di, can fiya luwa, nyinangum Yulangum yora.
\v 45 La con tuten kange kebceb niber wo bwira la ceu bou ciko na ci yi nyo, la cwile nii wo an bwira la wo fiyau, a yila nyo kange kaldo bwir ko wuro.
\v 46 La Yecu dibo tokka kereko nubo mwerum cineneu ri, nece kange yitobcebo bou tim kale, cwiti na cin to co.
\v 47 Kange yico, “To nemwe kange yitub mweb tirangum kale, cwiti na ci tok ker kange mo.
\v 48 Yecu yi co nii wo yico kereu, we nemi, we yitub mibo?
\v 49 La con taar kang ceko fiye be bei tomange ce nineu yico, “To” buro co nemi kange yitob mibo.
\v 50 No nii wo ma diker temi wo di kwama cwitiye ri, nii cuwo co nemi co nemi kange yitob mib.
\c 13
\p 
\v 1 Ki kume cuwo Yecu cerum luwe nen, yan yiken kong caji.
\v 2 Nubo kila, kila mwerkani cinen la con doken mor na bire mwenge con yiken more ce tangne nubo ducce tiranken konge.
\v 3 La Yecu yici dikero kila-kila or dangke. Con yi ci “Nii fike kange yaken fik dumek.
\v 4 Kambo co fi tiye ri, kangum dumembo yarangken nure, bilibatine bou cibangum cuwo.
\v 5 Kangumbo yaranken fiye terentiyeu bitine mani yorau tabbo bwi cin kim wori bitine cuwabo.
\v 6 La kakuko kwiuri cin comam wori ci manki niyeten cin kucom.
\v 7 Kangum dumembo yaranken tiber cuiyaktini, la cuiyakko dwiyangum di cakkangum ci.
\v 8 Kangum dumembo yarangken bitine ken, ma nuni kangumbo kwini kwob, kangumbo kwini nukkun, angumbo kwini taar.
\v 9 Niwo ki tuweri ca nuwa”
\v 10 Bibei tomange bou yi Yecu “Ye bwi mo yi nubowo keroti mor dangke?”
\v 11 Yecu yii ci “Kom wi ki nure wo ka nyimom yurke liyare loh kwama, la ciye ci nencibo.
\v 12 Niwo cike an neten co naci fiya ducce, La nii wo mancike, bi dure cinneu an yumom cinnen.
\v 13 wori co dike bwi mi yici keroti ki dangke. To na ci ti toi ri mani ciya toti, tano citi nuwei ri ma ciya nuwati kaka nyimom.
\v 14 Cine neu dike Icaya to tokeu dim. Wo tokki, no mo nuwatiri, mwan nuwa la mani mo nyomti, toka kan to mani ka nyomti.
\v 15 Wori ner nubo wori wi ki kumtacile bwai na ci nuwa, cin kumom nuwe ciye naci tore ki nuwe ciye kaka ci nuwa ki tui ci kaka ci nyimom ki ner cir, la naci yilau nan twam ci.
\v 16 Nuwe kime iker bibwiyer wori cin to, tu kime wori cin nua.
\v 17 Bilenke mi yi komti nob dukumeb kange nubo wucake ducce cin cui naci to dike ka towe, ci tobo, cui naci nuwa diker ka nuwa ci nuwa bo.
\v 18 Kom nuwa dangke niwo ya fi fikeu.
\v 19 No kangumbo fulen liyar kwamar nyombe ri, nii bi cirene an bou bo yuwom dike ci finer cereu. won co dumbo ci fi nureu.
\v 20 W ci fi fiye bitine ki terentiye, co niwo nuwa kero ri yuwa wulom-wulom ki for neret.
\v 21 La wori ci man ki niye bwici can ti biduwar la no co fiya kalaka kange dotange ri, wulom-wulom co yarum.
\v 22 Wori ci fi mor cuiyakeu co niwo nuw kereu la cuikko kalek kange kiyemer cakacangum kero la co mabo.
\v 23 Dumbo wo ci fi bitine keneu, co nii wo nuwa kero ri, nyimome ma ken kange kwini kwob, kange kwini nukkun, kange kwini taar no wo ci fi ciyeu.
\v 24 Yecu bo cinenten ki kang dangke. con toki, “Liyar kwamaro ki no na nii wo fi dumbo kem takeceu.
\v 25 La nubo da dumtiri, nii kiye ce bou fiti yerako wi mor bikate ce, la cu ce.
\v 26 Kambo Cuiko duyom meri, la ma ce bitwiti ceu ken
\v 27 Cangam nii take bou yi co, nii dur, mwe fi bo dumbo ken take mwe ka? Man nyi yerako wiye?
\v 28 Con yi ci “nii kiye ma we” cangam cebo yi co, la muki cui nyo ya nyo kubangum ka?
\v 29 Nii take kii, O-ong, no com kubang yerako tiri kang kubangum ten kange bi kateu.
\v 30 Kom dobci gwam ciya dwi nyo gwam ya cinko bika. La no lam bito ri man yi nob bitobbo, “Kom kwon yerako ki kaba, kom bwam ki blak na kom twim, kom mwer bikateu mor bini mi.
\v 31 La Yecu bo cinen ten ki kange dangke. con toki kii, Liyar kwamaro nan nun bikate (Musta) wo nii kange tu ya fi ta kece.
\v 32 Nuni wo co bi duware gwam tannen nunim bo nin. La no dui ri la tannem nunim bo gwam, yilam ti wo bilibe dii kwama an yulng loni ciye kani ce nin.
\v 33 Yecu yi ci kange danke tak, co tur duwo mim taca taare na fuu ci gwam.
\v 34 Gwam dike boro Yecu yi nubo mwerume kin dangke, co cibo kange diker wo kebo dangke.
\v 35 Wuro na yilam dike ci toke nyii nob tomangeb, ba na dim, wo co yi ki, “man wumon Nyii mi mor dangke. Man tok dikero wo yurangum. yurange nawo a yom fer-kur kalereu.
\v 36 Yecu dobom nubo mwerumeu. doken mor luwe. Bibei tomage ceu cinen cin yi co, Fwetan nyinen dangke yere wo takeu”.
\v 37 Yesu ciya la yici “wo fi dumbo keneu, so bi bwe nii fireu.
\v 38 Takeu so dor bitinero, la dumbo ken ko ci bi bei liyar kwamaro. yerako co bi bei nii kiyeu.
\v 39 Ni kiyeu fi fikkeu so bwekelkeleu. Bitou so cuile kaleu, nob bitobbo ci nob tomangeeb kwama wusake.
\v 40 Nyori yerako ci macangum ci tuimeu co cuile kaleu.
\v 41 Bi bwe nifir an tom nob tomangeb kwama wusakeu ci an bwabangum naci cokum liyar kwamar gwam dike buro dok bwiran ketiye kange buro wo mani bwanten werfun tiye.
\v 42 Ci an merken ci mor kra cillen, fiye ciya ci wiyeti kange kironka nunnek.
\v 43 La ubo wusakeu ci an buwa na kakuk mor liyar kwama teciye. wo ki tuweri, can nuwa.
\v 44 Liyar kwama nan cweka yurangum yurange takeu. Nii kange fiyari yurangum cu ki bilangtum, yan miyem dike co cikeu gwam. La tiyenum take wo.
\v 45 Takeu, liyar kwamaro na nii kyeme do yoryore tiye.
\v 46 No co fiya kange wo yoryore ri, co ya ci miyem dike co cike gwam co tiyenum.
\v 47 Nyo tak liyar kwama nan bi liyar ci mer wima, la mweru dikero ducce.
\v 48 La dim ri nii taka jinge ko kwou konge, La con yiken con mwerum kenko mor kole, Bwirtinim bo ci miranwi firen.
\v 49 An yila nawo fiya co kaleu a bou ti cwileu. nob tomangeb kwama wasake an bou chokum nubo bwirko mor nubo wussake nen.
\v 50 Ciyan merkeng ci mor kira cilong-cilonge fiye ciya ci ti ka wiye kange kironka nunek.
\v 51 Ka Nyimom dike wuro gwam ka? Bibei tomange ceu ciya co, “Ong”
\v 52 La Yesu yici “Nyori nob merankar werunero, wo yilam bibei tomange liyr kwamareu, ci nan nii ki luwe wo yeu dikero sarko kange fwirko mor kwene ceu.
\v 53 i fo nyori Yesu dim dangke brori, dubom fiye curo.
\v 54 La Yesu doken biten ce, meran nobo nen mor bi kur wabero Ursalimau. Nyori cin nyimange ciki “Nii wo fiya nyomka kange yileng do wo fe?
\v 55 Nii wo kebo bi bwe nii kwaka luwe ka? kebo nece ci cuwo ti ki Maryamu? Ale yakubu kange Yusufu kange Saminu, kange Yahuza kebo yitub ceb ka?
\v 56 Ale yitub ceb natubo kebo wo kange be ka? ca dikero wo fe?
\v 57 Cin kangum ner ducce dor cer. La Yesu yi ci “Nii tomange kwama mani fiya dur loco kange mor nubo loce.
\v 58 Ca mabo nyimanke ducce wori ci nebo bilinke.
\c 14
\p 
\v 1 Ki kwama curo Hiridus Liya nuwa fulen Yesu.
\v 2 Yi canga ce kange Yuwana wo yu mwemti wusakeu kwenu tuwe, wori Bikwando wo ma nage tiki co.
\v 3 Wori Hiridus tam Yuwana bwam co ta ke merken co furcuna, ki ker Hirodiya wi yi ce Filibus.
\v 4 Yi co ki daba nyo tu co na wi mwe.
\v 5 Hiridus kin twalum co di laki cwa tai nobe, wori cin tu co na nii tmange to dukum tire.
\v 6 Di kakuk boka Hiridus kentanguu bi bwe Hirodiya yel yila kwo yoryore kabum Hiridus.
\v 7 Co ma cinen mor kange weri ki ca ken dike co cwitiye can ne co.
\v 8 Bwiko co nuwa ker necerori con ya coki aneco dor Yowana wo yu mwemtiye mor fantilaner.
\v 9 Liya mam funer ki keni cero kweri wori weri co mane, nobo wari kange co fiye cika nin co bwi co yi ki a ma nye.
\v 10 Con twom mwati ka dor Yuwana ro furcina.
\v 11 To mi a mwatu doro co ya ci boki dor cere mor fantilane ci ne bubya co ya na neken nece.
\v 12 Bibei tomange ce to ci tu bilendo ya cin fwerum. Kambo naceu Cin ya la cin yi Yesu.
\v 13 Yesu nuwa nyori cerum tkum mwengem bo nin ya yiken ki kwace fiye kange. mwe kankanko nuwa nyori cin bwang cinen ten ki na mor cinan lor.
\v 14 Yesu bo kabum cem to tenanka mwerka nobe ko, cii cimen, co twam nubo nuwabo luma mo re ciye.
\v 15 Ki Yo me bi bei tomange ce bo ci yi co, fiye wuro kiye kume no kweri fim, yo mwerka ko wo na ci ya cunnukur na ci tik dur ciyero nen cari.
\v 16 Di la Yesu yici ki wifini yame ciye man kom necci dige ciya ca tiye.
\v 17 Cin yi ki nyori carito cwendo nung kange jinge yob koni.
\v 18 Yesu yi ci ki kom bu men ciko.
\v 19 Yesu yi mwerka nobe ciya yiken dor yeret co tu carito nunge kange jinge yobe, con kunge dii kwama yoti bibwiro wi, con ne bi bei tomange ce.
\v 20 Gwam ciye cin ca cin bwam, ci to fiti cari kange jinge bulendo kwob cilombo yob.
\v 21 Nubo ca, nabarubbo bikate nung, kiyebo kange natubo. kange bibeiyo
\v 22 Can nawo con yi bibei tomange ce ciya doken mor tokum mwengem bo, na ci yabken dinge wineu. nimde co beri na co yo mwerkako.
\v 23 Bwiko co yo mwerkako cuwe, co ci kwiken dor bange kwobka dilo kume fim co firen ki kwace.
\v 24 Can nawe tokom mwemero ki no tiber wimar, bwayum kaka koti ki mwelanka mwengero kange Yuako ne ci dotangeti.
\v 25 Ki kume (kene tar na kume ce) Yesu meru dor cinen yauti dor mwenger.
\v 26 Bibei tomange ceu to co yakenti dor mwenger cin cwa ciko ciye ke keno kelkeli, ci kwa kiyange mor tai ye.
\v 27 Di la Yesu yi ci ker can nawo co ki kom ma bi kwan neret, mo kom nuware tai.
\v 28 Bitrus kari ki teluwe tano mo ri dok ye bo fiye muneneu dor mwenger.
\v 29 Yesu yi co bo, Bitrus ceru mor nabire mwenge yauti dor mwemer Yesu nen.
\v 30 Bitrus to Yuwa ko taito tam co fiya co ter dikako co teluwe fulo ye.
\v 31 Can nawo Yesu tarkanko tau Bitrus, yico ki mo nii bilenke bi dob, ye bwi ner mwero oktiye?
\v 32 Bwiko Yesu kange Bitrus donken nabire mwenge co yuko yiloten makake.
\v 33 La bibei tomange ce mor nabire mwenge ci wab Yesu ci yiti ki bi cum mo bi bwe Kwama.
\v 34 Ci yabum cin lau biten Janisata.
\v 35 Nubo wiye nyomom Yesu, co ci tom tomange mor cinanlor, take ci bo cinen ki nubo ki buwarakeu.
\v 36 Cin ken co, ca ciya cimen na cin tai bwi belle ceu, gwam wo tai ceri fiyam luma.
\c 15
\p 
\v 1 Kangeb nob dinglib kange nob mulanka ci bou fiye Yesu wiye, fire Ursalima ci yi ki.
\v 2 Ye bwi bi bei tomange mue kim diye nobo dur biro matiye? mani ci nir kanci nime ci ca cari.
\v 3 Yesu kari me ci, kume ye bwi kom kim werfuner kwamare ki dike kom bwangten tiye?
\v 4 Kwama tok ki Nee tee mwe dur kange ne mwe. Nawo tok kro bwir dor tecer. kaka nece ri, tam ca bwiya.
\v 5 Di la kom ki gwam wo yi Tece kak Nece ki, tikali mo fiyati minen naweu luma kwama nen.
\v 6 Ni wo cwi bo co ne tece dur nure kom tu ker kwama yilam manki nage ker dike kom bwantentiye.
\v 7 Kom kulendo bwir, dong dong Ishaya tok ker dor kumer.
\v 8 Yi ki nubo wure ki niye dur fo tol niyeyer, ner ciyero kutan kange mo.
\v 9 Ciki wabye kone, wori ci merang werfuner nober, yi dige a bwanten tiki ciye.
\v 10 La co merkangka nobek fiye co wiye con yi ci kom ta cini kom nyomom.
\v 11 Kebo dige doti nyi nii yilati ki duyie dige ceruri nyi nii, co no yilanti dutiye.
\v 12 Bibei tomange ceu bo co mo nyomom nob dinglibo nuwabo luma ci nuwa kero wa?
\v 13 Yesu kari yi ci fikko wo kebo Temi diye fiye, an kwom co.
\v 14 Kom dobti nyo cin fukma ti kabo tiye. tana fukma ta kece fukma nin cweri, gwam ciye ciyan yarken buwak.
\v 15 Bitrus kari yi Yesu, fwetang nyinen dang kewo.
\v 16 Yesu tok ki kom ken kom yomba?
\v 17 Kom toba dige doti nyi gwam yakenti fureu, nyo a erti yaken tek bunak.
\v 18 Dike ceruti nyi ki ceru mor nere, co dige nii yilati ki dutiye.
\v 19 mor nee kwabanka digero bwir cirutiye, twal ka duwe, kayaka, Bwirangtum, kwii warkere cwerke kange tor kanganka.
\v 20 Kangem bo co diger kang nii tiye ca ka kange buni nerka kange mni kang nii.
\v 21 Yesu cokbon wi yaken yare cinan lor taya kange Sidon.
\v 22 Knage nawiya kan aiya bo wi fiye cuwo, kun diro kibi kwan ki nuwa cire duwe mi teluwe bi bwe Dauda, bwe bubya mi ki ni mor dotange fir kange bwekelkle.
\v 23 Yesu kar cienbo ker, bibi tomange ce bo kenan co ciki yoken co bwang binen ti ki kiyange.
\v 24 Yesu kari tok ki ci tomyebo fiye kange wiye, ci tom ye kwamae lemle wo lo Israila.
\v 25 Con bo con cunge kanbom cem, co tok ki ki Teuwe tekang ye, kari tok ki daten a tu tii bibeiye a ne birin bi cuwe.
\v 27 co ki nyo Teluwe birin bicuwe ki cam fitiwo curu kan nii luwe.
\v 28 Yesu kari, yico nawiye bilenke mwe tenangi kabo. na yilamwen kambo mo cwitiye. Bubya ce fiya luma dang cang.
\v 29 Yesu dobom fiye cuwo yaken bi dom kange wima Galili, co kwiken diale la yikenwi.
\v 30 Mwerkankako dutce bo cinen bo cinen ki, nobo mani nuwatu tiye, fukma, kilen kange nobo nyiyo tamtabe, nubo dutce. Kange nuo nuwa bo luma cin bo ki ki kabum yesu co ci twam twirak ciyeko.
\v 31 Nyo nubo kila yimati ki wo ci to nu o nyi tamtabe tok ket tiye. kilendo la yayamti kungando fiya luma fukma ti toi co ci dukton kwama
\v 32 Yesu c bibei tomange ce cinen la tok ki ma ci noboti ci wari kange mo kume taar, ci manki diye ci a catiye, ma cwibo nyo ci cabo cari kari ci fumom nure.
\v 33 abibei tomange ce kar cinen ba fiya carito fe, wo alam na bom nubo wo tiye.
\v 34 Yesu ki cirito kwem to nyi kom cike ciki niber kange jinge kilabo.
\v 35 Co Yesu ii nubo a yiken bitine.
\v 36 Tu carito wo niber kange jinge, bwi koko coma buka kange, con wuangum curito co, ci ne bibei tomange ce, bibei tmnge ne nobe.
\v 37 Nubo gwam ca cin bwam, ci mweran fiti cai bulendo niber dim.
\v 38 Nubo ca ci bi kate naw ka nabarub, kiyebo natib kange bibei.
\v 39 Yesu yo nubo doken nabire mwenge taken yare magadan
\c 16
\p 
\v 1 Nob dingli kange Sadukiya ci b cinen, ci cwiti na cin cwa co, cin kenc co ca nung cinen yirombo ii kwama.
\v 2 Kari yi ci ki meri, kom ki fiye an lumi wori dii kwama fiye je.
\v 3 Ta ke ki bwiri kom ki fiye lombo, wuro dii kwama fiyeje, dim dii ka? kom ynomom kabel yirom dii kwama la kom fwe ki jyomka keneko.
\v 4 Kaldo bwir, nubo man ki taka bwiti, ci do yiromti di la yirom kange man wo a nungtiye ka wo Yunusa ce”. Yesu cu.
\v 5 Bibei tomange ce bo dinge wureno di la cin tabum ci tu bo cirato.
\v 6 Yesu yi ci kom cibi kom yiki bati, kange dige fuu nob dinlibo kange Sadukiyawa.
\v 7 Bibei tomange ce yateen ti tokkan bwiti ci, keno wori cari mani di.
\v 8 Yesu nyomom co yi ci ki kom nob bwinin bilenke, ye bwi kom tokkan ti bwiti kume, keno ker carito bo, bocikeri?
\v 9 Kom nyombo kom bulangbo carito cendo nung wo ca ki nobe bi kate nunge, bulen di nyi kom mwere?
\v 10 kaka carito cwendo niber, nubo bikate na'ar, kange bulendo niber, nubo bikate na'r kange bulendo nyi kom tume?
\v 11 Ye bwi kom fwe ki nyomkako kom ki kebo cari ma kom cubi kom ka bati ki camfuwam, nob dinlibo kange Sadukiyawa.
\v 12 La wo ciya bulangti, tok bo amfuwambo mor cariye di la ki yi ci ciya cub merangka nob dinglibo kange Sadukiyawa.
\v 13 Fiya Yesu bo kai cariya Filibus me bibei tomange ce, wobo ki tok bi bwe nifire nyi?
\v 14 La ci ki “Knagem ki yi ki Yuwana nii yuka mwenge, kangembo ki Iliya, kangembo ki Irimiya, kka win mor nob tomange.
\v 15 Yi ci, kume we kom yi ti ki me?
\v 16 Saminu Bitrus ciya kari mo Almaciya, Bibwe kwama ki dume.”
\v 17 Yesu kari yi co nibi bwiyer mo Saminu bibwe Yunusa, kebo nange kange bwiyale fwetang mn dige we Te mi mor dii kwama.
\v 18 Ma yinenti mo Bitrus dur tere do wo ma mo bikur wabe mi tiye. Nyilo bwiyare man a fiya turinikiditti dor cer.
\v 19 Man nenen yilo dii kwama ko diker mo bwabi fo kaleri, yilam bwambwabe firen dii kwama. Dikero mo kwim fo kale, yilam kwim firen dii kwama.
\v 20 Yesu yi bi bei tomange ce ci ya yide nii con Almasihu.
\v 21 Tabti fo Yesu ter yika bibei tomange ce tamyo co ya Ursalima co nuwa dotange dutce kan nubo durko nen kange nubo dur wabero, kange nob mulangka werfunedo, ci twallum co an kun co dume bwiko kume wari.
\v 22 La Bitrus yaken ki co cungagin werangco, ki wuro a kutangi kange mo teluwe, wuro mani a bwiti kange mo.
\v 23 Di Yesu yila Bitrus, yila kenbwi mi, bwekelkele. mo ter kottanka minen, wori kwom nen bo kange diker na kwama ce ka na nubo ce.
\v 24 Yesu yi bibei tomange ce ki ni wo cwiti na bwagmentneri ca ko dor cer na co tu bwatiye bware ce na co bwangmenten.
\v 25 wuro cwiti naco fulo dume ce ri, co lemco, Wo lem dume ceri dormire di can fiya ti.
\v 26 Ye yori ni na fiyam kaleo na lem dume ce? Bibwe nii an bo mor duktanka Te cer wari kange nob tomange cak-cak ke, nimde na ya nubo gwam dor dike mo mane.
\v 27 Bibwe nii an bou ki luma te ceko kange bibie tomange ce, an ne nii dikero ca mani fo kaleweu.
\v 28 Bilenker mi yi komti, kangem komem bo tim feu na mani twi bwarti, Di ci an to bibwe nifire boti mor liyar cer.
\c 17
\p 
\v 1 Ki kume nukkundi Yesu tu Bitrus kange Yakubu kange Yuwana yiciye yaken ki co bangko cweem cwemeu, ki bwico.
\v 2 Yirom cembo tii ba kabum ciyembo tikob cebo, ti bibai na kakuk, kange bellece ti tibai na filang.
\v 3 Katten di Musa kange Iliya cerkangu cinen, tak.
\v 4 Bitru kari, yi Yecu Teluwe yori bo fo fiye wo bo wiye. Tona mon cwitiri man ywel bi kurdo tar, win kimo win ki Musa, win ki Iliya
\v 5 Co mor takka kerer biloro tia nyi cumo co diro coro bi loromi yici kiwo bi bwini mi cwiye coni fumen nen tiye kom nuco.
\v 6 La bibei tomange ce nuwa yori cin mwelken dorcero bitene wori cin cwatai.
\v 7 Yecu bo ke ci yici ki kweni kom nuware tai.
\v 8 Ci kum dore ciyero, cito bo nii.
\v 9 Fiyaci yirouti bang Yecu nyiki kom yire ni dukkum bowo fico bi bwe nii kwanen.
\v 10 Bi bei bwangka ce me ki yebwe ni mulanka a tok ti ki Iliya yo boteye?
\v 11 Yecu diye cinen ki Iliya an boragu ki dikero.
\v 12 Di miyi kom ti iliya kweri bou dila ci yomkombo nyori cin macinen diker ci cwiye. nurewo, bi bwe nifire an nuwa dotange kan ciye.
\v 13 wo bi bei tomangece ci nyme ki tok cine kero tok Yuhana nii yuka mogen.
\v 14 Ci law fiye mwirkanka ko weyenri kange nii bo cine, cunguge kabumce toki.
\v 15 Teluwe ci bi bwemi wori ki juwe takeu, nuwa dotangeti kwabi ki yalti mwem kange kira ngit.
\v 16 Maboki ci bi bei tomange nin cin dor bo twaka.
\v 17 Yecu, Kari tokki nom bwini birinke kange cwatanka kle fiya fiyang mayi ti ki kome ko bo ki co fiye mi wiye.
\v 18 Yecu kwenancinenten la ning bwice celum bwi fiya tai ka?
\v 19 Bi bei tomange ce bo Yecu nen yulum yurang me ki yebi nyo fweki co kake?
\v 20 Yecu yiciki bilenker kumero nyo bi duwar mi yi kom ti naki kam wii ki beilenker na nun bi katairi kam nyi tiyo kamki kwam yaken fire tiyo an kom dike kange mani wo ala bi gwamm ki matiye.
\v 21 La iren kelkeliyo wo mani a certi ciya kwobka dilo.
\v 22 Ciyim Galili, Yecu yi bei tomange ce ki ciyan ne bi bweni kan nii.
\v 23 Ci nyi mom twirum co ki kume tar an kwenum bibei tomange ceu nero kayam.
\v 24 Ci lam Kafanahum nubo yo dortiyeu wumer cekeltiyeu cin bo Bitru. ciki nii merankakumeko, ne wumer cekeliti. Na dore ce?
\v 25 Co toki ong dila Bitru do ken mor luwe Yecu ter kero kange co, nye mo kwatiye Saminu? liyam karero ciki nyo kemer doren wine kika kemer mweng fiye nobfuwai.
\v 26 Bitru kar cinen fiye Fabubo wiye Yecu yic nyori citu nob finyige keben yakako dila kari.
\v 27 Bi don nyo ka doreka bwirangke, kam ya wima, mam ker bibumo kom tau jinge wo ter bo kakeri. tano kom wom niceri, komfiya cekelo kumtu kone nubo yodoro tiyeu mi kange mwin.
\c 18
\p 
\v 1 Ki kwama co bibe bwingka Yecu me ki co wining durko mor di kwama.
\v 2 La Yecu co bwi bi duren kange tiber ciyer.
\v 3 Ki miyi kom ti na kam yirambo na bi bitiuttiri mani kom kuti di kwama.
\v 4 Na ni wo yoken dur cero na bwi bi duwareri cu dikero dur ko di kwama.
\v 5 No kom yo bwibi duware wo ki den mir di kom yomye.
\v 6 Wuro dok win mor bibeiyo wo ne bilengke bwiranke, la diker a ye cinnen ti ter nerer kwir cer, na merken. Co wima cuwa.
\v 7 Gwam dor bitinero, wo kwantangka a fiya ciye gwam wiwo kume ni wo abotiye.
\v 8 Na kangmweko kaka namweko an donen kotankeri mwatum co di mirangco wi. Na wori La mwen diker kange wo ciya tunken nen ti kira ki kanko yobeu, Lamwen diker do lokwama ki kanko win ko nako win.
\v 9 Na nuwe mweu an dok nen kwentanka ri cokum co na mirank cowi fiye mwi wiyeu an lamwen diker mo doken dume ki nuwe win kange yarka mor kira ki nuwe yob.
\v 10 Kom burange kom cwinkande bibei bi durti nen bo bibwe tomange kwama to ti com tii ciwo di kwama.
\v 11 Bi bwe ni bou na cok dike lemeu.
\v 12 Ni ye burangeka kime bou? na nii ki kwamagwini kom win la win reb maciya dubam tenwini ter cuo tereti naco dou woreme ka?
\v 13 Na fiyam wo winenri miyi kom ti furner cero an lawo kuni tereo co dobeu.
\v 14 Yo na wori yori kebo di wo tekume wo dii kwama nuge naco kun mor bi durdunen dowo na bwiyam.
\v 15 Tano kenmwe kom mwendi yico tiber kumer mokange co kub biyo tano nunenddi moyirau.
\v 16 Tano kam nukang bo bwitikimiri, kiya ki nubo yo kaka tar naci yiram warke, fi nob warka ko yau be kaka tare nunge kiro gwam dong dong.
\v 17 Na ko nuwa ka ciye kori ya cuko nob kwama bone nako na nuwa ciri. tuken co na nubo yombo kwama.
\v 18 Mi yi kom ti dike kom bwam bitineu bwam bwabe di kwama kike kom wineri gwin-gwine di kwama.
\v 19 Mi yi kom ti na nubo yau an ciya ki dike kom kinantiyeu te mi wo di kwama an makimen.
\v 20 Fiye nubo yau kaka, taar ci mwerum ki denmireri mi we kange ci.
\v 21 Bitrus bow Yecu nen ki kwama kiri to nyi kemi ama men burang ke manciten wiye? in lam kirito ni bwirka?
\v 22 Yecu diye cinen ki mi yi nen bo mii kirito niber, miki niber kiriti kwini niber.
\v 23 Nyori liyar kwamaro kino na liya kange o cwii naci kiyem kemer cereu knage cangam cere.
\v 24 Kambo ci ter ri cin bow cinen ki canga kange wo ci bwang tenti talent do bikate kwobbe.
\v 25 Dila kambo ci man ki nureu ci yam tiyeri, te kuwece ne wrfunendo ca a myim co, kange wii ce kange bibeyo kange dikero ci cikeu gwam dila na yam nan cero.
\v 26 La cangau yarken bitine, cungi kabum cem la ki “Teluwe, ma biner kange mo, dila man yi nen dikero gwam.
\v 27 La teluwe canga co kambo cin dim ki cikakeu nyem kang cinen di la citang cinen nan cero wi.
\v 28 Dila canga co cei ya fiya kange kece canga, wo ci bwang ten denani ti kwini kwob wiine cin tam co ri yoten bukka ceko la ciki yam ye dikero mi bwang mwne ten tiye.
\v 29 Di la kece cangau yarken bitine la kinog co ki “nuwa bi neri kange mo, ri man ya tinen wi”.
\v 30 Di la canga wo ki kaba ko, Nyori, cin ya ci merken co mor fucina no cin yam co dikero ci bwang cinen ten tiye nyimde.
\v 31 Kambo kebcebo canga bo to dikero bwiyeuri, cin kangum ner duce cin bou la cin yi teluwe ce dikero bwiyeu gwam.
\v 32 La Teluwe canga co, cou co rila yico “mo bwe canga bwir, mi tab mwen dikero mi bwang mweng ten tiyeu gwam, wori mwin kinong ye.
\v 33 No mwiki nungbo kemwe nin cireduwa, na wo min nung mwen cireduwe?
\v 34 Teluwe ceu knagum ner duce la neken co kang nubo ne dotange tiye no ciyam gwam dikero ci bwang cinen ten tiyeri nyimde.
\v 35 La nyo Te me di kwama ama kimen tiye ken no kom cutangbo kebkumebo nin wi mor nere kumer ri.”
\c 19
\p 
\v 1 Lam bou kambo Yecu dimkero buro di co ca dubom Galili con yaken ti yii kar Yahudiya, dinge caji Urdune.
\v 2 Nubo kila-kila bwan cinneten con twan ci finange cuwo.
\v 3 Faricawau bouragum cinen ci cuwancoti ciki “daten nyo nii kambo wer funen nageu, ni a twal wii ce nin naaka ki kange dikerka?
\v 4 Yecu Yii ci ka kiye bi wika tok ki co ni wo fule ci fiya kabu fuel, ci yob bwayile kaange nawiye.
\v 5 Co niwo fule ciyeu tok ki kiwuro nii an dubom Teece kange Nee ce na murom kange wee ce, ci yobeu cin yilam win.
\v 6 Ci man yob tak la buiyo win Na nyori dike kwama mureu, kange nii a yalkande.
\v 7 Co ci yice, “La ye bui Musa yinyo ki nyiyal nyo tual nawiye nin na'aka nyo ywaco take?
\v 8 La co yici bikwan nerer kumer, co dok muca ciya kumen ko tual nawiyenin Na'aka ki kaba kebo nyo.
\v 9 Ma yi kom ti nii wo tual wii ce nin neu naka, na kebo borutom.
\v 10 Bibei tomangeceu yico nawo nyo nii kange wii ce di, yorbo a na'aka.
\v 11 La Yecu yi ki “Kebo kwarub a yo merang kako tiye, la kan co nubo cia cinen cia yowe.
\v 12 Kangem wii wuro bou ci Teeni (Combilome) Nyo tak di kangem wi buro yilamTeeniu ki ker Liyaro lo kwama. wo a yo merangka ko wo tiyeu ayo.
\v 13 Co ci bou cinen ki bibeiyo biduwatinim na ci yo cinenkang dor, kwob cinen dilo, “La bi bei tomange ceu erang ci ti.
\v 14 La Yecu Yii ci, ko dob bibeiyo bidu wattinum bo ko ywa cire bou kako kami wori liyaro lo kwamau ki wang ciko.
\v 15 La con yoti ka'ani ceu dor cir na nimde co dob fiye co.
\v 16 La nii kange bou fiye Yecu wiye tok ki “Nii meranka, nangen do ken do wini ma matiye nan fiya dume dii yeu?
\v 17 Yecu yi co ye bwi mo meye kerti dor nangen nero kene? win cuwab dong dong, no mo cuiti mo do ken mor dumedi, bwnag ten wer funero,
\v 18 nii co yii co ki wer funero wini? Yecu yico “Tuwalde nii mare buro tum, kuure kwi, ma'are warke niyer ker,
\v 19 Ne Tee mwe kange Nee mwe dur, na cui nii bi dom kange mweu na dor mwer.
\v 20 Bwe bwantn yile wo yi co, mim man buro gwam yee ma mati take?
\v 21 Yecu yii co, na mo cuiti na yilam dong dong di, ya'a miyem dike mo cike gwam, na kabkang nob bune bo nen di na mon fiya ciwekako dii Nimde na bou na bwanten ten
\v 22 La be bwa yile wo ki fir nerer wori con nii cuwe cuwe.
\v 23 Yecu yi bi bei tomange ceu, Bi com ma yikom ti, a yilam bwai yo na nii cuiwe-cuiwe na do liyar kwamar.
\v 24 Yila ma yi ten komti an la telem bo min a doken buwak bilifirak kange wo nii cuiwe -cuiwe a do liyar kwamar tiyeu”
\v 25 bibei tomange ceu nuwa nyori, yila cinen ki nyomanka bicom cikii we a fiya cerka tiye?
\v 26 Yecu to ti cici, fiye nubo wiye man i a mati, la fiye Kwama wiyeu dikero gwam ki maman.
\v 27 Bitru karu ki, Nyon dubom dikero gwam nyon bwangten nen. La ye ya fiya tiye?
\v 28 Yecu yici bi com ma yikom ti, kom wo ka bwang men teneu, ki boro fuir ko kwama wo bi bwe Nii a yi kenti kutile Duktangka ceu, kom keneu ka yii dor kutileni kwob cilombo yobe nin, kom ma tuwe luweu kwob cilombo yobeu Iciraila nin bolangti.
\v 29 Na nubo dubom loni, yitob cib, bayilob natub, Tee Nee, bibei kange tanki ni ki den miredi, an fiya kirito kwini kwob can fiya dume dii ri Yeu.
\v 30 La nubo ducce buro kabou na weu ci an yilam buiyok, nubo ducce wo buiyeu ci an yilam kabak.
\c 20
\p 
\v 1 liyar do kwama ki na nii Ta'ake kange wo cerki kimuomje do nob nangeneb buro ama nangenti taake ceu
\v 2 kombo ci tokka ngum kange nob nangenebbo ti naiyo win ki diye, ci tung ci taake cecia ma nangendo
\v 3 lacon certen ki kam kaneko tereu lacon to nob nangeneb kangem tirangum konimiye kulenek
\v 4 laco yici ko ya'a tabke mi man ne kom dike dong dongeu co ci ya cima nangende.
\v 5 yika con certen tak ki kang keneko kwob yob, con fiya kangem co ma na kabau
\v 6 yila con certen ka kiyaka naku ked, co ya con fiye kange nob tiram koni laco yici ye bui ka tirangum koni na kwam kakuko we?
\v 7 won kange nii mani wo tu'u nge. lacon yici kom keneu ko ya ta'a ke mi
\v 8 kanbo mee lame di nii ta'akeu cou betomangene ceu nob nangeneb na ya'a ci nan nangener ciyero, terti nubo cuwa bwireu naya ciko nobkababo.
\v 9 kambo nob nangerneb wo ca tu'u ciki kumji yadi lane ci naiyo win-win.
\v 10 kambo nob nangeneb kababo bou weri, cikwati cina ocum nyo la ci keneu cone ci naiyo win-win.
\v 11 kambo ciyom nan nangener ciyereri, laci ti funan dor nii ta'a ke donin
\v 12 cikii nob nangenebbo wo cowa bwireu ma kan kenko wimbiwine fiye nangne la yila mon tu'u kenci dong-dong kange nyo, wo nya twal bwiyeu kange cilon.
\v 13 la nii ta'a ke kari yiciki farub, ma ma kumembo kange dike kebo dong-dong geu ka ciya men bo kama naiyo win-win ka?
\v 14 Tamdike na mweu na ta nure mweu. macui co ma ne nob nange nibo cuwa bwireu dong-dong, na wo mane komeu.
\v 15 wendi kebo dong- dong nama dike cuiye ki dike namiye ka? kaka kor kamatiye ki dike mamani dong donge ka?
\v 16 cuwo nyo, nob bwikob cia yila nob kabab, nob kababo ayila nobo cuwa bwireu. conubo duccu nubo biduwar kwakwabe cokcoke
\v 17 kanbo Yeecu yakenti wurcalima di con yaten kange kwob cilombo yobeu cungeca, dor mirer laco yici.
\v 18 ko to bo ki kwin mor wurcalima, an ne ken bibwe nifire kan liya nob wabeb kange tual kak
\v 19 cian neken co kang nubo kumtacilib na ci buo cona malli co, na kungum co
\v 20 la weebe beyo lo Jabadiu bou Yeecu nin kange bibei bayulobe ce yobe beu co cung cunge naco la con me kange diker cinen.
\v 21 Yeecu yico yee no cuitiye / lacon, toki moki bibeyo lomi wo yobe ayi, win kangko catiyere win kangko mokere, mor liyare mwe.
\v 22 la Yeecu yico mo nyom dike wo mo metiyeu. mon dolum mo nomki kwelmwenge woma dadom nokaka? lacin yii co nyan dolum.
\v 23 co yii ci kwelmwenge miu cuwo kan dolum noka, layimbo kangko catiyere kange mokeu, ke bo ma ne tiye, na nubo buro na ciye teemi yuelum yuele.
\v 24 kambo tanggnim bibei tomangeceu kwobeu mwo wodi, cin man funer kange yitob bo wo yobeu
\v 25 la Yeecu coci fiye cowiyeu yii ci kom nyom liyabbo tam ki nubo kuntacili yeu nung cinen liyarti, nubo dorko cinen loreu nung cinen bikwanti
\v 26 mani ayilati nyo tiber kumer. tano nayori nii wo cuiti na co yilam du'ur more kumedi tamcan yila canga kume.
\v 27 la nii wo cuiti na co yilam nii kaba kumedi co a yilam canga kume
\v 28 kanbo bi bwe nifire boubo na ci co dur, lana cone dur na co ne ken ten dume ce fanka nubo kila-kilau.
\v 29 la ci cer jenko, mwerkanka nubeko ducce bwang cinen tene
\v 30 la cin to fukmatini yob yirongum kong nure, la fukmatinim bo nuwa Yeecu ciu tiyedi, lacin kung dirciro citi toki, Teluwe bi bwe Dauda nuwa cini nyeu.
\v 31 la nubo ca cinen tor yii ci cia kamangum. kico nyeu, fukmatinim bou wo, yokten kung ka direk ciko laã wo kwatti yeu, tokti Teluwe bi bwe Dauda nuwa cini nyeu.
\v 32 la Yeecu tin cok, cok, doki cin cou ci, la me ci ye co cuiti nan ma kume ne?
\v 33 co ci yii ce, Teluwe nyo cuiti na nyo fiye to ka fiye
\v 34 la Yeecu bulangi ciko neercer, coke nuwe ciyeu. ca canduwo cin fiye toka fiyek. yila cin bwang ten co
\c 21
\p 
\v 1 kanbo Yeecu kange bi bei tomangeceu dadom kange wurcalimari, ci yaken betafaji fiye bang jaitun ne. co Yeecu tuom bibei tomange ce ci yob.
\v 2 co yii ci ko doken muan loro kakumeu, kan to kelba kange be ce ci wari. ko kwiu ci kom bou men ciko.
\v 3 na kange nii yii kom dike kange dor nyo di, ko yi co Teluwe cui citi. nii co an tomu kom kici danjang.
\v 4 wo mani nyo na din dukum nii duku membo toke
\v 5 ko yi bi butobo ci yo na, ko to liya kume bouti kumen nii cukka duwek yim dor kelbar dor be lunjuge kelbar.
\v 6 co bi bei tomangeceu cu yaci ma dike Yeecu yi ciye.
\v 7 ya cin ki kelbau kange be kelbau ci miranti kulenciro cere, Yeecu kwii la yii ti dor kulenro nin.
\v 8 dur nuber mirang ti kulen ciyero dor nurer, kangem bo kiyangu alu tiniu cin miranti nure.
\v 9 nubo mwerum we kaco kange buiceu, cin kung dirciyero citi toki Hocana fiye bi bwe Dauda wiye, ni bibuiyere co, wuro bou ti mor dene Teluweu. Hocana fiye Teluwe wiyeu,
\v 10 kambo Yeecu doken wurcalima cinarloro dim, la ci merangi we wo?
\v 11 nubo lankar cinen, won Yeecu, nii durkume wo Najaret mor Galili.
\v 12 co Yeecu, doken mor bi kurwabere, con yuwabkan nubo miyaran diker tiye kange buro ten dikerti moreu. co yalangum dengila nubo wo fuion kiyemer tiyeu, kange kutile nubo miye nagum fiye tiyeu.
\v 13 con yii mulangum mulange lomi a yila lo dilor, lakom yilam buwak nob kub ciko.
\v 14 co fukmatini kange kilenti bourangu cinene mor bi kur waber, con twan ci.
\v 15 lanob bi wabero durko kange nob meranka werfunereu, cin to diker nyumankaro wo co manange cin nuwa tenbibeyo ci kun dirciro ti mor bikur waber, tokti Hocana fiye bibwe Dauda wiyeu, cin nuwa buwarum nem.
\v 16 coki yii ce, mo nuwa dike ci tok tiye? Yeecu ciya ci oo laka nuwambowika, nyibibeyo bi du wadinim an buro no yiir tiyeu man dokti dur tangkako wi?
\v 17 la Yeecu dubom ci cerum mor cinan lor yaken betani kuma co ca da'a wi.
\v 18 la con buri kanbo ca yilau cinan loreri co nuwa wuranti
\v 19 la con to tii nyingcin kong nure, con ya dimertironin laca fiya bituti mani kan layu. lacon yii tiye, betuti no nin we munen tak, danjang ko cuwo tii nyingcin dor kwicim
\v 20 bibei tomange ceu tonyori, cin nyumangi ciki manyi tii nying cindo kwiddim dangjang nye.
\v 21 Yeecu yila yii ci, bicom ma yii kom tii na kom wiki bilanke kwaneri manidi, kebo ka ma tii nyingcin do nine ka ma tiye, lakom toki bwen nan co bang ko wori, kom ki akom co dii, na mob ken mor caji, la an manyo
\v 22 bwen na yeka keneri, kone bilenkerirti, kam nyo.
\v 23 kambo Yeecu bou mor kur bi waberedi, liya wabe nubo dur nubero bonrangn cinen kambo co ma meranka tiyeu, cin toki, ki bikwan kerero wuni moma dike buro tiye, we nenen bikwan kero ce?
\v 24 la Yeecu yii ci, na miu keneu man me kom ker. na kom yii yeri, man yii kom keno ki bi kwan kerero wini ma manan dike buro ti cike.
\v 25 yuka mwengek yuwanako yau fe? yau dii kwama kaka, yau nubo nin? la cin tokkangi bwiti ci, ciki na bou yii boki dii kwama an yibo, ye bwi ka ne nebo bilener kange ce?
\v 26 bwen bo yi bou ki bou nubo nindi, bou cuwa nuboti, wori ci gwam citu Yuwana na nii dukume.
\v 27 co co la ci yii Yeecu ciki nya nyombo. co keneu con yii ci, mikeneu mani ma yii komti keno kibi kwando wini ma manangum dike buroti yeu.
\v 28 lan ye ka kwabe? nii wi manangen do take duwen
\v 29 bweu yii co mani ma ya ti, la ki con fulong nercero con yaken.
\v 30 la nii wo ya be yobe nin tok dike co yiwo kabau. lacon manciya Tee laco yabo.
\v 31 wemor be beyo wo ma dike teciye cuitiye? ciki wo kabau, Yeecu yii ci, bicom ma yii kom ti nuboyo dorti kange nob burotume an do kenten liyar kwamaro namimde kom.
\v 32 Yawana bou kumen kin nure cak-cak ka ne bo bilenker kange co nubo yõ dor tiyeu. kange natub ma burotum tiyeu ne bilenker cinen. lakume bwiko wo ka tom dike wo mane, ka yoloten bo ki bui nako ne bilenker kange co.
\v 33 ko cuwa tu kange danke. ma kange ni take, con fi fik take nin, con kwarum takeu, con wob bicunge yamka inabikowi, con mu dengila cuwen cuweme wo atom take tiyeu, lacon neken nubo kangem takeu kambo ci tokkangum kiyemereu, lacon cu kange bitine kange.
\v 34 kambo cuwa kiye inabi ko lameri con tom canga ce kangem na yo cinen carin cari to co mor takeu.
\v 35 la nob nangenebo wo tacanga buro buk wineu, ci tualum wineu, mobang wine ki ter
\v 36 nii ta'ake tung ten kangem cangam, lawo ki kabau, la nob nange nebo ma cinen na wo ki kabau.
\v 37 bwiko cuwo nii taãke tuom ten bibwe ce, cinenr, tokti
\v 38 kambo nob nagenebo to bibwi nii ta'ake di citi tokkangi buiti ci, won co nii aca kwali to tiyeu kom bou bi twalum cona bou cam kwalito,
\v 39 la cin tam bweu, ci mobkenco buim taken laci tualum co.
\v 40 la nii ta'akeu boudi, ye cama nob nangenebo wuro nin tiye?
\v 41 la cin yico, an tualangum, na yila ta'ake ne nangene bo bwirko buro ki mare cilong cilonge, na yila ta'ake ne kangem nob nageneb buro a yam co tiki cuakiyar inabikeu.
\v 42 Yeecu yii ci ka tobo mor bifimere, tero wo nobo nin kuweti koweu, coyilan ter culangere. woki no Teeluwe nin, la yilam diker nyiman kar nuwebe?
\v 43 na weu ma yi komti, antum liyar kwamaro kumer, na bitine wo ne bituti tiyeru.
\v 44 nii wo yarti dor terero wori can yakcangum ki fiti. la nii wo tero yae cineti dore di ankuwan co.
\v 45 la nii liya re kange faricawa cin kwa ki dike ci toktiyeri la cin nyom ki tok kange ci.
\v 46 ci do tika cekori, lacin cuwa tai nubo mwerum meu, wori nubo tum co con nii dukume.
\c 22
\p 
\v 1 kiritti yila yici kerti ki dangke. cuki
\v 2 liyar kwamaro wi tami liya kange wo yulang bi bwece nin ci ka nakakke.
\v 3 nyi bi bei canga ce bou ker na kakko, la cin ko boka.
\v 4 la nyori liyar yila tomten ci kangem nob canga, cokikere ki yi nubo wuro ci yi ci kere to, min fweten cikka ko min biye nenne kange bi cit biyeti tak direro gwam fiyam na cikka ce
\v 5 la nubo tubo kero ki bilangka cin tab ka nure ciye kange take ce kange fiye tiyen ka kange miyeka.
\v 6 tang nim bo cin cangam liya. cin nuwa cinen cin twal ci
\v 7 la liya nuwa funet. con tomi ciya cuwo cinen nob bwaka dekeb ciya twallangum nubo twal nube naci twim cinar lor ciyero.
\v 8 la cin cangace cika dim fwelka di. nubo wo fiya tomange ci datenbo
\v 9 na no nyori kom nure kom cangangu nubo kwarub wo kom fiya
\v 10 wo yori nyeu kange yorbe lo liyaro dim ki nob kambo ken.
\v 11 kambo liya bou naci to fabubeu cin to niwo dor bo kulen cika
\v 12 di liya nyi co farmi mu manyi mu doufo fiye wuro kulen cika mani ye? ni curo fwe ki ker tokk.
\v 13 laliyar yi bi bai canga ki bwam ni wuro kang kange cna naki merken co mwor kumtacili fiye wuro manki wiye kange kuka nunek.
\v 14 nyo nubo ducce ci cuwowe la bidob ci cokke.
\v 15 dila nob dinglib cin fuwau kutume kanbo ciya taco ti tokka kercere.
\v 16 la cin tung ciclen bi bai canga ciyeu hirudiyawa cin yi kiritti. ni merangka nyin yumom mu ni bilinke yulo mu merang nubonin kero kenti yonen bo wi kange ker nuber nyo tok mu man ki cuika darek mwor diber nober
\v 17 di la nyo kermwero? daten yi ya dorer kai care kakka yi yare ka?
\v 18 lan Kiritti nyi mom funer ceyiro yici ye bwi kom me yeti nyo we kom nubo bwir.
\v 19 kom nungmen culom ki yemero curo la cin bo cinen ki kiyemero
\v 20 Kiritti yici nyo komne
\v 21 kaicar dige yilam nace kwama dige. yilam nace
\v 22 kambo ci nuwa nyeri yila ci men ki, nyi mangka, la cin dob co cin cu
\v 23 nyo yinidi nob bwiran kerero kangem wo liyabo kange kwenka kaleka cin bou cin nen cin meco
\v 24 ciki ni meranka muja tokki no ni na nacoiye bwiyam man ki bwedi yice na yi kange wice na bo bibwi
\v 25 kangem ciyem bo wi nyo nukkun wo ki kaba na lan bwiya kam ci man kibi bei yeu dob kechenin wice
\v 26 yice wo yobeu co kenneu co manyo la wo tereu yaken cuko nubo ni beri nin.
\v 27 wi bwi gwam ciye la na wi yeu bwi gwam di la ki kakuki kwenka nob bwareb na wi yeu ca yilam wi we mwor nubo nukku nin? nyo gwam ciye na co
\v 28 la Kiritti ci ya yici ki, kom lem, dige biwiyeu kom nyombo bifumer kakka bi kwan kwama
\v 29 dige bwiyeu kwenka nob bwarebo naka mani la mani ciya mwer kang citi naka.
\v 30 nona curo nyori ciki nona bibei tomange di kwama.
\v 31 tano dige yilam kange kwenka nob bware yikom bwangtenbo dige kwama yikoma
\v 32 cuci kwama a brame kwama Icaku kange kwama Yakubu? kwaka kebo kwama nubo bwiya kwama nubo ki dume tinin.
\v 33 kambo tare nuwa nyeri ci men ki nyi manka.
\v 34 dii kambo fariciyawa nuwa kiritti ywa cudu ki yawa di la cin mwer dorciyero
\v 35 ki bwo fwer ciyer kange nubo nyimom bwo langeu cin cuwa co ki meke na ci nyimom co.
\v 36 nimerenka fwer funka mwor bwolang?
\v 37 Kiritti yico bilang kwama mwe ki bi kwan mwero gwam kange mer mwero gwam kange mwor ner mwero gwam
\v 38 wuro co wer fundo kendo
\v 39 werfundo wo yobeu tami na mwe bilang niwo bi dom kang mwe na dume mwe
\v 40 dor werfundo gwam dawi kere ci tikeu nin.
\v 41 kanbo bi bei faracayawa ci murangum fiye wine kiritti meci ker
\v 42 tokki, nye kom kwati kange bi bwe kwama? co bi bwe we? cin yico bi bwe Dauda
\v 43 kiritti yi ci la manyi Dauda mwor yuwa tangbe cuwo ce bi bwe tokki
\v 44 bi bwe kwama yi bi bwe kwama yi kangko catiyer mer. la mai yila ke ki nob ki ye mwe ki no fiye fuwa namwek
\v 46 ni kange mani wo kar cine kange ni kar ciriren bo kerwi kange meco bo wi tak ka ciko dicire
\c 23
\p 
\v 1 la kiritti yi tartare kange bi bei tomangece
\v 2 coki nob werfundo kange faricawa ciyim fiye muca
\v 3 la nyori gwam dige ci yikom makerii kom mani wuro diger kimer ki tam yora dila kom mare dige ci manang tiye wori ci tkang dige ti mani ci manangti cuko.
\v 4 cibwa kulen tunyoti, wuro bwai tukakke ci tu mwer nubo nin lakgwom la ciyeuw ki bwi ci mani ciya tar biwure ciyeti tu
\v 5 gwam nanange ciyero cikin manin nubo nato ciki cur bi la ciye bi fumer ciyero ce ki tokko ci kwirang cunga tinin beileti.
\v 6 ki cwi yulangka fiye ti nin yimem ciyem tolnyiyer kange yulangka fiye yime ciyeu bikur kwama
\v 7 kange yarume yaruma na wa kungum dore fiye miyeka kange tiyenka na ciya cuwo citi kini meranka
\v 8 la kebo wo ciya cuwo kom tini meranka nyonin dige bwiyeu ni meren kakko win kom cike, kom gwam kom bi yitinim.
\v 9 ki cuwore ni kange teki kume fo kalewo dige biyeu tee win kom cike, diki nodi
\v 10 kom ciya ciwo kom de nobbifime dige bwiyeu ni bi fimer ki merowin co bi bwe kwama
\v 11 di ni wo yilam dur tiber ki nureu na yilam canga kime
\v 12 gwam niwo kung dor mwor dige gwam niwo tubo dorr cere ci kebo kange ni dur
\v 13 di la daten bo nyo nob mulanka kange faricawa nubo bwit kom ten nubo nin yilok doka lo kwama kom dobo kom dobbo nubo cwi doka tiyeu na dou
\v 14 daten bo nyo kom nob mulanka kange faricawa nyo kom nuwa natub kwilibti do tange
\v 15 da ten bo nyo kom mulanka kange faricawa nobo bwit kom bwilangti digge wimer kange tineni du wonka ni merangka win bi wine na ki kom fiyam kom mamco konidi lengtidi yulan kumero nyo di yilam ni kere ne kom
\v 16 da ten bo nyo kom fukma bo yame kom wuro kom tokti niwo werum kange ku kwamari kebo kange diger lagwam niwo werum kange mwindo ku kwamari weri ce fiyem fiye yime.
\v 17 kom kula fukwa tinim na wini la bidwi yere mwindo kakka ku kwama wiyeu na wo manki dwitiye mwindo
\v 18 tano wo werum kange tanjilandowu cakke kebo diger tano niwo werum ki kiye mero ci yoti dor cereri weri ceu tomco
\v 19 kom fukma ti nimbo na wini wo durke kimer ku kwama kakka win mwabe wuro mwer kwama nin kiyemer tiye?
\v 20 tano nyo gwam niwo werunki tanjilando wucakke werum gwam co kange dige dorcere
\v 21 tano niwo werum ki kwamari werum kango co wo fwer cereu
\v 22 tano gwam niwo werum ki di kwamari liyar kwama kange wo yim dor cereu
\v 23 daten bo faricawa kange nob mulang kanb nobo bwit kom cokkom luma renek ywerek kange kule kange lam cur la kom mirang bilengke wuro tu nyo weu. yona wucak, cire duwe, bitinke cu wura daten ka matiye kebo na wuro kom cutang. tang nini bo wiye
\v 24 fukma yame mwem nuwa kungkunge nin kange dige kangem nyori mwon mim tecembo
\v 25 daten bo kom nob mulangka kange faricawa nubo bwit kom nir bwim kwimkwelmwengeti kange kwele la mordi dimka bwirangke kange fitrerer
\v 26 no fukma nubo bwit ter yiwelka bwim kwele kwelmweu na bwim ciyemba yimki yorak
\v 27 daten bo kom nob mulankab kange faricawa nubo bwit na tuweti nim kumembo tami bitine fwor wiye kum ma curo nobo to yaran kume ko kale firer mwordi kom kuk nubo bwiyam kanga dwiti dimer kidimen
\v 28 nyo fo nuwe nobo kom la firer mwor di kang bwirankeret kange nero fit mwor.
\v 29 daten bo nyo kom nob mulang kab kange faricawa kom ki tuwe nob dugumeb la kom yulangum tuwe nob bilike
\v 30 kom tokti komki no yitin nowi ki kwama teb nyebe nin nonyiti necibo filan curka bwi yale nob dugume
\v 31 na curo nyeu nung dor kimero kom bi bei kwalka nob dugume
\v 32 di la okm dim cuwa ka kwama
\v 33 na cweti nini kom bi nob bwit mana ka dorti nokom bwolang kwama
\v 34 tano nyodi to, mitom ki men nob dugumeti, kange kange kanlangnbo kom twalangum kangukab ci naci kulkenki kam ma kangam bo benjange kurbi wubit kumer kom bwanten citi cinat lor cinar lot
\v 35 maka ko nyeu dige kom manange dwiti bwile nobo kendo gwam wo curi fo kaleweu yileken fo dor kimer tau fo bwiyale tabila yaken cuko zakka bi bwa bara kiya wuro kom twqlum co tiber kur bi wubir kange tanjilan do wuca ke
\v 36 bilinke miyikom tiye gwam niwe ca kung kutume ti dor nubo kalewo
\v 37 urucalima, urucalima mwo wuro twanong nob tomange miyila mu bang nubo ci tom mwemeu ki terertini kiritti nyi min cwi nan murangu nen na wuro bi cake ki muragu de bi bei yo loce tibir tangum ceme munko
\v 38 nwo cin nob kimen lokume fwengteng
\v 39 minyu mi yikoti mana ka toyeti tok, no ki diye ki tokkeri, bibwiroyo ati dor niwo bouti kiden teluwereu.
\c 24
\p 
\v 1 Yecu cire bi kurwaber ta nure ce, bibei tomange ce bõ ci, nung cinen muka bi kurwabero ti
\v 2 di, kari ciya, kom tõ dige wo gwamma? ke ti, kange ter meni na wo a dorke cer wo mani awertiye.
\v 3 fiye co yim dor kang zaitun, bi bei tomangece bo cin yuranum yurange, ciki ye a yila yirom boka mwetiye kange dika cwile kale.
\v 4 Yecu ciya, yi ci kom de kom tiyangum.
\v 5 nobo durce an bõ ki denmir ci yan to ki kimo almacihu, take ciyan dok kangem kila tiya ngum.
\v 6 kan nuwa fulen kwerer kang ka dir kwener, kom cubi, okm nuwa tai, tamyo dig buro bwi, dila cwila bwiri,
\v 7 ber an kwenan kange ber nin ten liyar an kwenang liyar nin ten an ma wura kange mulcaka bitinek fiye kidimen ki dimen.
\v 8 di gwam buro kabak buwarum bõ ka koni
\v 9 biko wo, ci an niken kom dotange nin, ci twalum kom gwam bero an kwer kom ki ker denemir
\v 10 fo dang tang kila a kottang tiye, ciyan kwerkom bwiti, ci ko ciya ka bwiti
\v 11 no curkebo kila a kwenu tiye ciya dur kali to tiyangum.
\v 12 timi bi cirin cwika ko kila anyibom.
\v 13 dila wo mwirumum meri an fiya fuloka.
\v 14 an tok fulan diyar dorbitinero gwam, be na yilam warka dor nobo nyombo kwama. nimde cwile bõ
\v 15 di na kom to dige wo nidurkume Danieltok ker cere, tim fiye wucak ke [ni kiyetiye na nyimi]
\v 16 buro yahudiya ciya cukken dor, bangnge,
\v 17 wuro dor luwe diye ca yirare na co to kange diye mor luwece
\v 18 niwo take ca yilau de lo bõ na co tũbeke ce dur ko
\v 19 kwan nobo tom ki bi bi bei kange nobo nẽ yir tiye fo kumeni wo
\v 20 kom kwob dila cwaki kume ko a yilare yuko bau kange bi diye kume fobka [acabaci]
\v 21 an ma dotange tẽnan tenange wo mambo wi ka cik fwelka kale wo yau ciko dwen. o-on mana wuro ti tak.
\v 22 na kebowo ci mwatum kumeri na kange nii man bũũtiye, ker nobo wo ci cukange, ci mwatum kume.
\v 23 tano kange yiki tõ almacihu wo kaka almacihu wuren, wo kom nere bilenkẽ
\v 24 wob curkebo kange almacian curke ci an bõ ci nung yirom kange deger nyomamka, an ci bol
\v 25 nubo kila yana kangi tana anmam di kange wo cukange. kom towa, mam yim kom tiya an bou.
\v 26 nyona cuwo, naci yi kom wuren kii kaka wuren yurangum kũũkom nere bilenka
\v 27 na wo mulankako tibati twar yaken cuko mẽ, nyo boko bi bwe nifiri a yila tiye
\v 28 fiye nange buyan buya wiye co fiye bicabuni ki mwer kande.
\v 29 di can cando wo bwiko kumeni dotange wo, kakuko an fin kumta cili, cwakko mani a nẽ filancekoti, bitirendo an yarangu firen dii kwama, bikwan wo nii kwama cin muka,
\v 30 nimde yerom bibwe nii firo an cirkangu for dii kwama, gwam nobo kalewo ciyan ma fir neret. cia to bi bwe nifire a bõmor bilore kibi kwan kange duktangka wo dwi nyeu
\v 31 an tom bibei tomange ce wo wucakke ki dir cumer kwamkwame, nobo co kwabe mor culangko na'ar tati wile dii kwama yaken coki wine nin
\v 32 kom tu merangka tii nyingcin do nin tana kan ceko yoten fuka, ter neka laluweko, kan nyomon tirakkon dadom
\v 33 nyo tano kom to dige wo gwam ko nyomom dadom, kino nyilok
\v 34 mayi kom bilenketi, kaldowo mani a cuti, dige wo gwam an bwi
\v 35 dii kwama kange bitine an cum, dii ker miro mani a cuti
\v 36 di la ker diye do ni mani wo nyome, nob tomange bo wucak dii kwama, kange bwe, kan Tẽẽ win
\v 37 nawo kume ni nuhu, ayila tiye ki boka bi bwe nifire
\v 38 kume ni wureno, nimde mwem cufana bau, nobo ti cai noi, citi nai, ci nakenti, diye nuhu doken nabire mweme
\v 39 cin nyombo kange diker, la mwembo, bo cam ci, nyo boka bi bwe nifire a yila tiye
\v 40 nobo you tim take, an tom win dobti win bwi
\v 41 natubo yob kwa nirti dor kannya an tom win dobti yim baim, wori kom yombo dige teluwe kume a botiye
\v 42 kom nyomom wuro, na nii kuwe nyomom fiyang nii kuye a boutiyeri na kin yi ki bati, mani a dob loceti, ci wuri ci doken.
\v 43 kom yiki bati, bi bwe nii an bõ fiye kom man ki nyomka
\v 44 we canga ken wo ki yilen ne, wo luweti, na neci cariti kambo datenni? nibi bwiyere canga, teluwece bo a fiya coti
\v 45 we canga ken wo ki yilen ne wo teluwe ce yo na to cinen luwe anneci, cariti kambo daten ne?
\v 46 nibibwiyere canga, teluwece bo a fiya coti
\v 47 mayi okm bilenketi teluwe ce an yoti co dor dige co cike gwam
\v 48 tana canga bwirko yi mor nerece, teluweme tabum bwi
\v 49 coter bukka tannum cangabo, co cati coti noi, kange tangnum nob nukabo
\v 50 Teluwe canga wo an yilau kakuko canga wo manki bati, fiya cuwo co nyombo
\v 51 teluwece an torangum co yob, cwile ce an yilam dong dong kange nii bwir tinim a yoco fiye cin wiye ti ka kuka nuneke.
\c 25
\p 
\v 1 la liyar kwamaro na bi butobbo kwobbeu wo tu talkire ce la cin yaken naci to nii kibineu
\v 2 nung more ce kuletini rila nug more ce yula kabo
\v 3-4 la kambo kuletini bi butobe tutal kire ceu ci tubo nuwango kange cinen dila bi butobo yula nyeu tu nuwanger cero kange calkiretini ceu
\v 5 lakambonii ki bineu tabum bwiyeri ci dugo dumti gwamceri cin darangum dum
\v 6 dila kina cii kumeri cin nuwa kwaka diregi to nii bineu ko ceri, nakom co gwam wabkanco,
\v 7 dila bi butobo co gam kwinangiri la cin ywellangum talkiretini ceu
\v 8 la kule bi butobeu yi nubo yula, kon ne nyinen nuwang kumeko bi duwar wori talkire nyeu lombamti
\v 9 dila buro yula nyeu ciya cinen wori mani a la nyinenti kange kumen ko ya nubo miye tiye nin ko te nu kumeu
\v 10 kambo ci yake tiyenkakeri nii ki bineu begen dila nubo ki batiyeu cu tange co fiye nakakonin dila cin nungum nyilogo
\v 11 kutang bori tangni bi bibutoi, bow la ciki te luwe, teluwe wom nyi nen
\v 12 dila cin ciya ciki bilenke mi yi komti mi yom kom bo
\v 13 nyori ko yi ki bati wori kon yombo diye kaka kwama
\v 14 la kino na nii wo darum na yaken mor bitine kange. cin co canga tini ceuri lacin neken dige ci cikeu kanceg
\v 15 win more ce cin ne talen ti nung, ki kange cine yeuri la ki kange tak cin ne talenti wiin la ci yorang talenti dong ikwan cer yila nii co yaken yamcembo
\v 16 la wo yo talenti nungeu yaken cuko win dor ken cii mor nangene lacin fiya mwem talntibo kange nung
\v 17 nyo takri wo yo talenti yobeu fiyau bo yob
\v 18 dila canga wo yo talenti win neu cu ya wob buwakko bitineri lacin yurangum kiyeme teluwe cero
\v 19 kambo kutangeri tee luwe cangetini co yilau naci kiye kemero kange ci
\v 20 cange wo yo talenti nungeu, bou ki mwem talenti nung tak. ciki te luwe mwi neye talenti nung. to min fiyau mwembo talenti nung tak
\v 21 teluwe ce yico ki yori kabo canga ken ki bilenke mwin ma bilnke dor digero bi dobeu matin yo nen dur dor digero duce dogen mor lumor talen mwek canga wo yo talen ti yobeb yau rki,
\v 22 teluwe mwin neye talenti bokange yob too min fiyau ten mwemb talent bo kange yob
\v 23 teluwe yico ki yori kabo canga ken ki bilenke mwin ma bilenke dor digero biduware matin yo nen dor digentiro duce digen mor luma te luwe mwek
\v 24 la canga no yo talenti wiineu yau la cin yiki teluwe min nyimom mwin cilongi nye. lamwiki biyem fye mwi fiibe nyori mwiki mwerumnyo fiye wo watangbe
\v 25 min cuwam tai rila ya min yurangum talenti meu mor bitine to wo digero na meu
\v 26 dila teluwe ce ciya lanyi co ki mo canga bwir, kange dilime mwin nyumom miki biyem fiye mi fibe take miki mwerum nyofiye me watang be
\v 27 nyeu mokin neken nubo ma nangen ti ben keme, mi yilau na weu miki yom kiyemer miro ki mwem
\v 28 nyori yom talenti cinen di na kom neken canga wo ki talenti kwobbeu
\v 29 la gwam niwo cikeri/ atin cobcinen ten la can yilam cuko duco. cike. dila kinii wo manki digereu, digero cimeneu atin tum cinen
\v 30 kom merken canga bwirko kale mor kumta cii fiye ciya ci wiyeti ki kika nunekeu
\v 31 ki kwama bi bwe nii fiye bow mor duktangka ceke kange nob tomangebo kangeceu, dila cin yii dor kutile duktangka
\v 32 ka bumcem an mweru bitinetini gwam,
\v 33 ca tin cikangum nubo win nawo nii bicire cokum dekwama mor nibetiniye catai yoken kwameu kamko cattiker, dila nebetini kanga mokke.
\v 34 dila liyau an yi burowo kango cattiyer ceu ko bou wo ko fiyer temi nineu, ca kwali liyarreko ci ywel kumen ki kwama wo ci yo kwar kalereweu
\v 35 wori min nuwa wura la kom neyi cari, min nuwa dilomwe la kom neye noka, min bow fabe la kom doken ki mo mor
\v 36 min ya kwancer la kom dumen kwileni min nuwa bo lumauri kom cib ye mi lofucina kom ya mini
\v 37 dila nubo cak -cakkeu an ciya ciki teluwe, fiyang we tonen ki wura la nyi camkimwe? kaka mwi nuwa dilo mwe tiri nyi nenen noka?
\v 38 fiyang nyi tonen faberi nyi cib nene? kaka mwi kwancer di nyi du mwilene?
\v 39 fiyang nyi to wi nuwa bo lumari kaka lofucinari nyi bou mwinene?
\v 40 la liyau atin ciya na yiciki bilenke mi yi komti dige wo kom ma wii mor-mor kebmibo bidu war tininbo wuro ninu, ko man ki mo
\v 41 la can yi buro kanko mor cekkeu, ko kubom min, kom wo ciikau ko yaken mor kire wo manki dikako ci ywel bwe kelkelenin kange nob bwangkab cekeu,
\v 42 worimin nuwa wura dila kom neye bo cari, min nuwa dilo mwe, dila komneye bo noka,
\v 43 min ya fabe, dila kom dobo kimo mor luwe, kwancer, dilakom dumen bo kulen, dam twirem kange lo fucina dila kom cib yebo
\v 44 la ciyan ciyaken ki teluwe, fyang nyi to ki wuro kaka ki dilomwe, kaka fabe, kwancer, kaka nuwabo luma, kaka focina rila nyi mwen bo nangenne?
\v 45 la can ciya cinen ciki, bilenke mi yikom, diger wo ko mabo kange nin wii mor bi duwar tininbo weri, kom ma membo
\v 46 buro atin go gen mor mwe kako manki dige dila nubo cak -caeu mor dume manki dika.
\c 26
\p 
\v 1 kombo Yeecu dim tok ke ti towo kange ciyeri co ca yii bei tomangeceu,
\v 2 kon nyomom kum kume yob na duklume yabkako na lami, laci an ne ken bibweni na ci kulken co
\v 3 lanob wabeko durko kange, nubo dur nubero cin mwerkangi karak nii wabero durko coti kikayafa.
\v 4 cin tokkangum nure ci tam Yeecu ti yurangum yurange na ci tallum co.
\v 5 la ci ti tokiki kebo ki duklumeu kati kwalkanke kweni tiber niber,
\v 6 kamob Yeecu ki no betanya lob caminu waleu
\v 7 dong dong kambo co yim cunga kobiomero ci cam. cori tiyeri, co nawiye kange dou kiwer nuwanger wo kikiyemereu cor Yeecu nin ti dorcer
\v 8 kambo bibei tomange cru to wo nyeri nercer. ron kaya, kim yebwi a yakcang wo ti nye?
\v 9 woro tin miyem ki kiyemero ducce na neken nob bune bou
\v 10 la Yeecu nyomom wuro lam yii ci, ye bwi ka ne nawiye wo dotange tinye? wo con mamen dikero yor yore
\v 11 kom kir-kir kange nob bunebo, la maka fiya, yeti kir-kir.
\v 12 na wo co corti nuwangko wo bwimi yeu, co mamna furka miko ce.
\v 13 bi com ma yii komti na fe atok fulen ke do wo tiye fo dor bitinero wo dike nawiye wo mane an toki ken na kwa ki co.
\v 14 la win mor kwob cilom bo yobenin coti Yuhuda kar yoti yeu yaken liya wabe nin.
\v 15 con toki, yemo cuiti mwa neye tiye naneken niwo kangmuek di? cin cuwa cinen mwin do kwini ta'ar.
\v 16 la nyeu con ta do ka nureko wo ca neken coti kang cikeu,
\v 17 la kume kaba wo duklume yabkako neu bi bei tomange ceu bou cinen, la ci me co, fe mo cuiti nyo yulangum na mo camcari durlume yabkaro we?
\v 18 co yii ci kom durlume cinan lor, kan fiya nii kange, ko yii co ni do mor ka toknyo kangkene takako dom, maca cari durlumer yabkaro lomo bibei tomangemiu.
\v 19 bibei tomange ceu mani kanbo co yii ciyeu, ci yuelagum cari duklume yabkaro.
\v 20 la ki mee con yii kange bibei tomange ceu kweb cilombo yobeu na ci can cari to.
\v 21 kanbo ci ca cari to tiyeri, con yici, bicom ma yii komti win more kume an miyem ye
\v 22 cin ma fir neorer, cinter meka ceko kiwinti min nyumom ke bomo na teluwe?
\v 23 la co yii ci, wuro dor kangti kange mo mor kwele wineu co nii a miye yetiye
\v 24 bibwe nifire an u kanbo mulangi dorcereu la kwanco nii kercer ci miye bibwe nii ye tin yor ni conin na cibou co bo di.
\v 25 Yahuda wo a miye co tiyeu me co, ma nii merangka? la con yi co, mon tokum ki bwimi.
\v 26 kanbo cica carito tiyeri, Yeecu tu carito yoten bibwiyer an kabkangum. con ne bibei tomange ceu, con tu cam wuro bwimi,
\v 27 con tu kwelmwenge, con ma buka kangek co ca nee ciye, yii ci ko nom gwam kume
\v 28 won bwiyalemi wo noro ceu wo corena tab ka bwiran kerer nubo kila-kila
\v 29 la ma yii komti, mani ma no mwem inabim bo wo ti tak mano kange okm fuije mor liyare Teemi.
\v 30 la ci okm nuweu, co ci cu bang jaitune
\v 31 la Yeecu yii ci, gwam kume kan kottangi ker mir ki kume wo, wori mulangum mulange. man tumom nii to tiyeu, kwame ten do an yalam
\v 32 la bwiko wo ma kwenunmeri, man yaken ten kumen Galili.
\v 33 Bitru yii co bwentano tangnim bo anyarangum ker mwer di, mi mani ma yarti
\v 34 Yeecu yii co bicom ma yinenti mor kume wo bicake na manb kiyangeri mon yi moki mo nyom yebo kirito ta'ar
\v 35 Bitru yii co, bwentano ma bweya kange mori, mani ma yiti mi ma nyomnenbo la tangunim bi bei tomange cembo tokti nyo ken
\v 36 co Yeecu yaken kange ci fiye wo co tike Getca maniyeu laco yii bi bei tomangeceu ka yim fo miki yankab ma koub dilo
\v 37 con tu Bitru kange bibeyo lo Jabadi yobeu, kange co, con ter bulankako kange tutum nerem
\v 38 la co yii ci, dumemi ki no mor bulanka wo a lamti ki mo bwareu ka yim for koma corka kange mo
\v 39 con kutaken tenkab biduwar la con yarken ki tikob ceb. laco kob dilo con toki, mo Teemi na an mamdi, kweie wo a cum ye, kebo mi a bwang tentiye la an bwanten dike mo cuiyeu.
\v 40 con yila bibei tomang ce nin co fiya ci dam dum lacon yii Bitru mo maka cor ti kange mo bwen na nang kenoko wina?
\v 41 kom cori kom kwob dilo kati ko yarken cuwaka, yuwa tangbe kwama kom ciya, la bwiyo kwambo
\v 42 coca yila yobece co kob dilo, con tok mo Teemi nona kwele wo cunin man nocori, be dike mo cuiti ye a mani
\v 43 con yilau ten co fiya ci da dumti wori nuwe ciyeu tu'u kabo
\v 44 con dubangum ci tak nako ta'areu, co kob dilo ti co tok tika dike kitanca tokeu
\v 45 Yeecu yila bi bei tomangkace nin, la con yii ci, ko damdum duwal komti fuobi? koto kwama con dadom, la cin neken bi bwe nifire kange nob bwiran ker.
\v 46 ko kwen bi ya to niwo a miye yetiyeu won lambi dom
\v 47 kambo co tok keretiyeu, yafuda win mor kwob cilom bo yobeu kange nubo dur nubero. cin bou ki kulenti kange kulki
\v 48 na weu, nii wo amiye Yeecu tiyeu tiibum ci yii ci nii wo ma teiceri co, ko tam co
\v 49 na con bou Yeecu nin con toki, yarume nii merangka laco tei bwiciu
\v 50 Yeecu yii co, farmi, ma dike mo bo makau, co ci bouwe ciyoti kanko dor Yeecu de laci tamco.
\v 51 la kange, kange Yeecu ter kan ceko coku kulendo cuwalum tu'u canga nii wabe durko,
\v 52 co Yeecu yii ce dokken kulen mwero fiye ce [loco] nubo wo tu kulene di a dwiya kin kulen
\v 53 mo kwatiri mani maco tee mi ti ya, la can tommer dike cum wenange kwob cilombo yobeu wo nob tomangeb cebo wucakkeu?
\v 54 la a ma nyi na bifumero na dim na wo tam nar ma nyeu?
\v 55 la Yeecu yii nubo dim wiyeu, ka bou kin kulen kange kulki bou ko ta ye na nii kwiye? mati yii ma meranti kir-kir kur waber la ka ta yebo.
\v 56 wo gwam ma nyo na dike nob dukumero na dimla bi bei tomange ceu gwam dubom co cuakkanyi cu.
\v 57 nubo buro ta co Yeecu yaken ki co kayafa nin nii wabe durko, fiye nob muiangkabo kange nubo durko mwerkangum wari yeu
\v 58 la Bitru bwang cinen tenti ku tan kange karak nii wabere durko con do ken mor co yii na co to dike a matiye
\v 59 na weu laya wabeu kange nob tikali cebo ki to warke cuerker dor Yeecu na ci tualum co.
\v 60 la fiya bo win wo. na duwaleu nob warker cwerkero kila bou kab.
\v 61 la ciki nii wo ki canwerum kur wabe kwamaro na co muti mor kume ta'ar.
\v 62 nii wabe kwen titiye lanme, co, mo man ki diker kar kaka? warke wini ci war ti dor mwere
\v 63 la Yeecu kumom. nii wabe durko yii co mo yii nen ti ki nyal kange kwama wo ki dumeu, yii kenon mo kritti bi bwe kwama
\v 64 Yeecu karcenen, mon to kum ki ko kab mon to bi bwenii yim kang ko catiyer bikwanrd, la yiranti dor bi loro dii kwama.
\v 65 la nii wabe durko worbangum belleceu, ki tok kero bwir, ye bwi bou do nob warker ti dualla? koto na wo kom nuwam kero bwirko.
\v 66 ye ko kwatiye? cin ciya ciki con daten buar
\v 67 ci tuom cinen ti bi tom bo tikob, yila cibukten co. ci kwabanco ki kani ceyeu.
\v 68 la ciki, yii bo ker dukumer mo kiritti. we wo kwa nene?
\v 69 la Bitru yim kale mor karake, la bubya kange canga bou cinen yii mo ki no kange Yeecu wo Galiliu”
\v 70 la Bitru kanangum kabum ciyem gwam tokti ki, ma nyombo dike motokker ti dorce reu.
\v 71 kanbo co cerken nyi lo ko kaleri, kange bubya toco la yii nubo wiyeu, nii wo ken kino kange Yeecu bunajare.
\v 72 yila con kanangum ten kange weri, ma nyom bo nii co
\v 73 kakten nyo bi budar di nubo wo tirangum wiyeu bou yii Bitru, bicom mon wi more ciye ken wori kero mo tok tiyeu nugum nen.
\v 74 la con yoten kan cilka kange weri manyombo nii co, ladanjang bi cukeu mob kiya ngeu,
\v 75 Bitru kwabi ki kero Yeecu tokeu. bicake na mob kiyangeu mwan kanang ye kiro ta'ar. la con cerken kale cociwiye kefir neerer.
\c 27
\p 
\v 1 kambo fini celummeri, liya wabe kanga nubo dur nubero cin fuwakang nureu ciya tam Yeecu ti naci twalumceu.
\v 2 cin bwanco, cin neken liya dur ko Bilatu
\v 3 dila ya fuda niwo nekenceu, kokacito ci war Yeecu nin bolang twal keri in do yiloka-yilotak yila cimen ki nungeu kwini ta'ar durem faricawanin kannge nubo dur
\v 4 yii ki mimmam bwirang ke ma neken buyale wo mabo bwirang keu la cin toki kii, ye yonyo wiye? nuwa ciko dor mwer?
\v 5 dila cutang culom nungemwi bitine ku wabe liyan dob ci, yaken yan yeiken dor cero
\v 6 dila ni durwabero tu culom nungembo yiki, kebo dnggdong mor werfuner
\v 7 la ci fuwakam keroco tibercer, kemero lacin te num ka fiye nii muka tinngek nin yilam fiye tuwe fabube bi ye kenwo mor tinnyere, kemer buyalr ka
\v 8 won co dike bwici cuo fi coti toti nyii Irimiya di duwenne kowo
\v 9 dila dike toki nyii Iremiya nii du kumeu diim cin tu culom nungem kwini ta'ar wo fene bibei Iccere, la yo dor ciro nin neu,
\v 10 cin neken na tenka bitinek nii tinngeret, nawo kwama yi yeureu
\v 11 dila Yeecunti kabum liya durko, liyadurko meco, mun liya yafudawarka? Yeecu ciya, nyoo mwa toke
\v 12 dila nob webebbo durko kange nubo durko cin mwelcinen, tokbo ker,
\v 13 dila Bilatu yico ki, mwo nuwabo mwelka tinim bowo ci mamen tiye ka?
\v 14 dila yicobo ker winwo, dike liya durko nyimanyi kambo ken
\v 15 liya durko nyamkang niwin nin nii wo nubo ma dacenneu
\v 16 ki kwama wuro cin wiki kange nii furcina deco Barnaba.
\v 17 la kaci muromere, dila Bilatu yici ki we kom cuiti a nya kumen kannge? Barnaba, kaka a wo ci cuwoti ki Yeecu kiritti ka?
\v 18 wori cin nyimwom cibomkico na kiyerce
\v 19 kanbo ciyim kutile twomcinen twomange ki, cirom nii wo nin nii manki bwaranke wuro min cokkan mor dukume kambo ken kercer.
\v 20 ki kwwamawo durem liya wabembo kannge nubo durko cin bolum nubo cin yi ki a nyani nen kange Barnaba nin, a twalum Yeecu
\v 21 dila dur liya meci kom cuiti a nya kumen kange? cin yi ki, Barnaba
\v 22 Bilatu yi ci ye ma ma Yeecu ninti woci cuwoti kiritti dila gwamceu cii ciya akulken co.
\v 23 lan yii ci, ye bwiye, bwiran kererde camane? di cin ciya ki diro duro dur, akulkenco
\v 24 kambo Bilatu to manica doldiker tiyeri wori kwobkanke atin kweni, duu mwembo nirim kemceko kabum nubem, yiki, mimanki bwiranke dor buyale niwo manki kwirankru komma dike komcuiye.
\v 25 nubo kwarub yiki, dila buyaleceu a yii ken dor nyo kange bi beyo lokyeun
\v 26 la nya cinen Banaba dila ma Yeecu nin balyanyeri neken co cinen na yekom co
\v 27 la nob dakkeb liya dureko cintu Yeecu cin yaken ciko mor luwe liyako dur, lacin murou tangne nob dukkebo ducce
\v 28 cin marancinen meke na nyime ci dokcinen kulendo fiyere.
\v 29 cin me cinen lalam duwek cuakkek cin dok cinenti dorcer, yila cineco dango ciya tam kamce ko cal ciyere cin cunyii kabumce ci ma ci nen buuomti, ci yi ti ki dume mweu akutan nyi liya yafudawar'
\v 30 cin tuomcinenti betuombo bwitak, ci yom damngo ci mweco ciko dor
\v 31 kam cidim buo kace keri, cin cokum lalango cin dok ci nen kulencero, cin cin ca cin kaba ya ken kica fiye ciya kulen cotiyeu
\v 32 kambo ci ciro kalere, cin kwabti bue ni bakurame kange dencero caminu, woci dokco ayakangeci natum bwatiye kulkake
\v 33 cin lau fiye kange ci cuotiki goltau, wuro yitiye, kweldu wee,
\v 34 cine neco mwem mwerum kange dike tweitweyeu naci nom kanbo citwiyeri lako nobo
\v 35 kanbo ci kulken ceri, cin kabkannyum belleceu kimaka dacenek dor cer
\v 36 lacin yiken ci too coti
\v 37 cin mulang dike kange cin yei ci nenti dor cer yiiki wonco liya yafudane
\v 38 cin yenkeco wari kange nob kub nyo yob, win neu kango cacci yerece wneu kango mwokece
\v 39 burombo cutiyeu too co t, fok doroti,
\v 40 laciti tokii, mwo muki mwom wurom lo kwamau yila mu mum mor kume ta'ar fulom dor mwero cile no munbi bwe kwamari yarau cuktom bwatiye nin
\v 41 nyoken durem nob wabebo macinen kange nob mulamgkab kange liyab bo durembo, ciyi tiki,
\v 42 fulom kangumbo la fueki fuloka dorek ceko co liya jorilawa. ciya yirau dor cuktum bwatiyem nabi ne bilinke fiye ciwuyeu
\v 43 kambo ca ciya kange kwama. kwama a cerco wori cinyi ciki cimbi bwe kwama
\v 44 nyo naco nob kubbowo nyo yob ci kulkenci wari yeu ci toce.
\v 45-46 ki kakukce kumta cileu cumuom bitineu kwarub yalam kene ta'ar na meece. ki kene taareri, Yeecu kun diro kibi kwan yikii, eli-eli lama cabak tani? ki tokki, kwamanin, kwamami, yebwi mu mirannye wiye?
\v 47 kanbo birombo timbo dmmen muwari nyeri, lacin yiki, nyi bicuor Iliyaro
\v 48 dangjang dangjang kange woom nacwak yatuu cukko dokti mor munge fuwar dokti dor damge tarcinen ciya nom
\v 49 latangneceu, dubomco nabito keno Iliya anbou na fulomcori
\v 50 la Yeecu kundiro kibi kwan cii neyee cola nyam kang yuwa tangbek ceko nin ne
\v 51 dila kuwabe kwama woram moro yob tamdi yiraken ciko bitini. bitrneu mikan nyi, bangtinimbo yaranngum,
\v 52 tuwe tinimbo wumangum, birombo wucakkeu darangum dameu cin kunangum
\v 53 cin cirangum mor tuwe tinim kanbo ca kwenum meri, cin doken cinar loro wu cakke cin yau nubo nin kila.
\v 54 ka dur nob dakkebo kange nubo wuro to Yeecu cin cwamtai kibi mikaka bitineko kange diko bwiyeuri, cin cwamtai kibi cuom cin yiki, bilinke wobi bwe kwama
\v 55 na tubo killa wofo Galili birombo bwangten Yeecu naci too ceu cin citi toi kutan
\v 56 morece mar yamu magdaliya, maryamu nee Yeecu kange yucufu, kange nii bibwe zabadi
\v 57 kimeri lani cwekaka ko kange inni armatiya bou, dencoro yucufu cekeneu inni bwanka Yeecu
\v 58 ya bilatunin me aneco bwi Yeecu dila Bilatu ne nyaldo aneco
\v 59 Yucufu tu bwi Yeecu cumuom ki lalango wucekke,
\v 60 la dokkenco mor tuweco ca wobi fwijeu mor la cin tungti tero nyi tuwe co cuwi
\v 61 Maryamu Magdaliya kange Maryamu wineu ciyim cunga ko wineri
\v 62 cilfiniceu nawo kume yulangka ko cumeu, liya wabe kange faricawa cin muri kange Bilatu.
\v 63 cin yiki, tee luwe nyim kwabi ki kwama wo ni bibolero wuro kidu meu toki kii ki kume taardi
\v 64 man kwenum nyori ne nyaldo a to tuweti na kume yo bbece kebo nyori nob bwanka cebo anbou kumco, laci yi nubo, in kwennm tuwe. la buoko an la kaba ko ceu bwiraka
\v 65 Bilatu yici kom tu nob to kabo kamma tokako kibi kwan kumer gwam
\v 66 la ci ya cito tuweti cin cumuom tuweu cin titi to ka kaning
\c 28
\p 
\v 1 ki kume kakuk fobka fiini, dadonm celti na kume winneu mor nibere. maryamu makdaliya kange maryamu, ya naci tuwe Yeecu
\v 2 la bitine muka ducce, wori yuwa tangbe kwama wucake yirau di kwama bou tungum tero, yiti dor cer
\v 3 yirom cembo na milbangka, la kulen cero na cuno
\v 4 nubo to tuwe tiyeu cwa tai duccu, cin yilam na bilenti nibe
\v 5 nob tomangem kwama wucake yi natubo wuro ki, kom cware tai min yimom kom ki do Yeecu wo ci yei bwatiyeu
\v 6 mani fo, kwenum na woco tokeu, tofiye teluwe daa wiye
\v 7 kom ya wulom, wulom kiyibi bei tomange ceu, kwenum nin, to wii kakom yakenti Galili ka fiya co firen to min yi kom.
\v 8 natubo wo wulom-wulom dubom tuweu, ki tai kange for nerero dur, cin cwa na ciyi bi bei tomange.
\v 9 la Yeecu fiya ci, ci ki yarume natubo bou tam naceko, wabco
\v 10 Yeecu yici, kom nuware tai ki ya kom yi yitob mibo ciya yaa Galilin ciya toye firen
\v 11 fiye natubo wuro mor yameri. nobo to tuwe tiye doken cinar lor, cin yi liya nob wabeko dike maneugwam,
\v 12 nob wabe kwama mwerkangi kange nubo durko, cin tokkan dike wo cange ci, cin ne nob toka tuweko kyemer duccu
\v 13 cin yi ci tanne nubeu, be bei tomange ceu bou bon kum bilen cero, fiya cuwo kom da dumti
\v 14 tona kero wo lam liya durkori, nyan ken co na daken ki ner cere fiye ki wiye
\v 15 nyori nob toka tuwe ko wo yuwo kyemero la cin mani na wo ci yi ciyeu kero wuro wati mor yahudawa yaken ciko duwen
\v 16 la ci bei tomange kwob culombo wiineu yaken Galili dor bangero Yeecu yi ciyeu
\v 17 la cin to cori, cin wab co, di kangumbo ciyabo
\v 18 Yeecu bou cinen, yi ci ker ki, bi kwamer liyaret cin neye dii kwama kange dor biitiner.
\v 19 kom ya ki dok nobo a yilam bi bei tomange ka le wo gwam kom yu'u cinen mwem ki den te, kange bwe kange yuwa tangbe wucake
\v 20 kom meran cinen ciya bwangten dikero gwam wo ma yi kom ki nyial leu to mikange kom ya ciko cwile kale. 
